desh%2C%20Indonesia%20and%20Pakistan%20concluded%20elections%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20but%20with%20serious%20questions%20looming%20big%20on%20both%20processes%20and%20results.%20The%20outcomes%20have%20raised%20fundamental%20questions%20on%20the%20progress%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20civic%20freedoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen%20can%20shape%20democracy%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%2014.1%20million%20new%20women%20voters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Fnearly-970-million-people-eligible-to-vote-in-lok-sabha-polls-says-ec-124020900957_1.html%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20registered%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20lead-up%2C%2015%25%20more%20than%20men.%20In%20South%20Africa%2C%20there%20are%20three%20million%20more%20women%20voters%20than%20men.%20In%20the%20UK%2C%20undecided%20women%20voters%20will%20have%20a%20significant%20say%20in%20January%202025%20elections.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20freedoms%20have%20been%20at%20the%20fore%20in%20the%20US%2C%20having%20already%20shaped%20the%202022%20midterms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20four%20nations%20are%20seen%20as%20global%20champions%20of%20democracy%2C%20none%20have%20fully%20%E2%80%9Copen%E2%80%9D%20for%20civic%20action%20or%20participation.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmonitor.civicus.org%2F%5C%22%3ECIVICUS%20monitor%20ranks%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20US%20as%20%E2%80%9Cnarrowed%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20a%20rating%20of%2065.%20The%20UK%20and%20South%20Africa%20are%20%E2%80%9Cobstructed%E2%80%9D%20spaces%2C%20following%20disappointments%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20India%20has%20the%20lowest%20rank%20of%20the%20four%20countries%2C%20a%20rating%20of%2031%20and%20classified%20%E2%80%9Crepressed%E2%80%9D%20since%202019.%20Among%20other%20evils%2C%20attacks%20against%20civil%20society%20and%20media%20legitimized%20and%20endorsed%20by%20the%20state%20stand%20out.%20There%20are%20no%20visible%20signs%20of%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaken%20together%2C%20these%20countries%20will%20choose%20leaders%20who%20will%20set%20or%20hinder%20a%20path%20of%20global%20prosperity%2C%20peace%2C%20climate%2C%20and%20human%20rights.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20choices%20made%20by%20voters%20this%20year%20will%20either%20strengthen%20women%E2%80%99s%20hard-won%20rights%20or%20cost%20them%20dearly%20if%20ultra-conservative%2C%20authoritarian%2C%20and%20regressive%20forces%20stand%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESlow%20progress%20with%20hurdles%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20progress%2C%20women%20still%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20representation%20at%20the%20highest%20assemblies%20in%20each%20of%20the%20four%20nations%20is%20at%20their%20peaks.%20But%20with%20women%20making%20up%20half%20of%20the%20population%2C%20the%20progress%20is%20a%20gross%20under-representation.%20India%20fares%20worst%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20decision%20makers%20with%20only%2078%20women%20members%2C%20or%2015%25%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20lower%20house%20of%20Parliament.%20In%20contrast%2C%20women%20make%20up%2047%25%20of%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20National%20Assembly.%20In%20the%20US%20and%20UK%2C%20close%20to%20one-third%20of%20the%20highest%20elected%20bodies%20are%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInequality%20is%20not%20just%20in%20political%20representation.%20Women%20earn%20less%20than%20men%20in%20each%20country%20and%20are%20often%20less%20secure.%20India%20again%20fares%20the%20worst.%20The%202024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwbl.worldbank.org%2Fen%2Fwbl%5C%22%3EWomen%2C%20Business%20and%20Law%20index%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20women%20in%20the%20country%20have%20only%2060%25%20of%20the%20rights%20afforded%20to%20men.%20The%20country%E2%80%99s%20female%20workforce%20participation%20stands%20at%2037%25%2C%20lower%20than%20expected%20of%20a%20fast-growing%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKBN1JM075%2F%5C%22%3EReuters%20survey%20ranked%20India%20as%20the%20most%20dangerous%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20world%20for%20women%20in%202018%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20signs%20of%20improvement.%20Nearly%20a%20third%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20women%20have%20experienced%20physical%20or%20sexual%20violence.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fcrime-in-india.html%5C%22%3E2023%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveals%20a%20distressing%20surge%20of%204%25%20in%20crimes%20against%20women%20in%20India%20including%20domestic%20abuse%2C%20abductions%2C%20assaults%2C%20and%20rapes.%20Although%20rape%20is%20now%20a%20non-bailable%20offence%2C%20those%20accused%20often%20walk%20free%20protected%20by%20those%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbroad%2C%20India%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forumarmstrade.org%2Fusindia.html%5C%22%3Eworld%E2%80%99s%20largest%20importer%20of%20arms%20from%202018-2022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20likely%20contributed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeacekeeping.un.org%2Fen%2Fconflict-related-sexual-violence%5C%22%3EConflict-related%20Sexual%20Violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20(CRSV).%20Women%20and%20girls%20continue%20to%20be%20primary%20targets%20of%20CRSV%20resulting%20in%20long-term%20trauma%2C%20humiliation%2C%20and%20broken%20communities.%20Because%20India%20has%20refrained%20from%20endorsing%20the%20Arms%20Trade%20Treaty%2C%20it%20is%20not%20obliged%20to%20assess%20risks%20to%20human%20rights%20when%20trading%20arms%2C%20including%20from%20and%20to%20countries%20in%20conflict.%20113%20states%2C%20including%20South%20Africa%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20have%20signed%20up%20to%20the%20treaty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202020%20UN%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeacemaker.un.org%2Fwps%2Fnormative-frameworks%2Fun-security-council-resolutions%5C%22%3ESecurity%20Council%20Resolution%20on%20Women%2C%20Peace%20and%20Security%3C%2Fa%3E%20(WPS)%20calls%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20peace%20and%20security%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%2C%20and%20assessing%20women%E2%80%99s%20needs%20in%20relief%20and%20recovery.%20India%E2%80%99s%20denial%20of%20internal%20conflicts%2C%20like%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66260730%5C%22%3EManipur%20violence%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20left%20no%20room%20for%20women%20to%20be%20engaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDespite%20the%20odds%2C%20women%20stand%20up%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20women%20have%20taken%20to%20the%20streets%20not%20only%20for%20themselves%20but%20also%20for%20citizens%20who%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20be%20Indian%20is%20questioned%2C%20persecuted%20LGBTQI%2B%20communities%2C%20farmers%20and%20workers.%20Women%20represent%20a%20powerful%20political%20force%20as%20citizens%2C%20voters%2C%20journalists%2C%20caregivers%2C%20educators%2C%20and%20more.%20%C2%A0Global%20movements%20such%20as%20%23MeToo%2C%20%23FreeSaudiWomen%2C%20%23NiUnaMenos%2C%20and%20%23AbortoLegalYa%20are%20examples%20of%20women%20driving%20positive%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20flaws%20notwithstanding%2C%20India%20has%20a%20disproportionate%20influence%20on%20international%20decision-making.%C2%A0%20It%20has%20a%20long%20and%20positive%20history%20of%20shaping%20global%20norms%20and%20standards%20on%20democracy%2C%20peace%2C%20and%20human%20rights.%20In%20international%20spaces%20like%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20and%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%2C%20India%20can%20play%20a%20key%20role%20reconciling%20BRICS%20%2B%20countries%20and%20the%20Western%20world.%C2%A0%20Given%20their%20history%20of%20decolonisation%20and%20action%20on%20social%20justice%20and%20non-violence%2C%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%20are%20well-placed%20to%20champion%20global%20democracy%20and%20human%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20women%20have%20the%20power%20to%20shape%20the%20future%20by%20voting%20for%20progress.%20It%20is%20in%20our%20interest%20to%20take%20a%20hard%20look%20at%20the%20options%20on%20the%20table%2C%20stand%20up%2C%20and%20be%20counted.%20Despite%20the%20long%20and%20challenging%20road%20ahead%2C%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Day%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20we%20must%20commit%20ourselves%20to%20positive%20change%20for%20a%20healthier%2C%20safer%2C%20and%20more%20equitable%20world.%20In%20an%20acutely%20polarised%20world%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20votes%20could%20be%20our%20best%20bet%20against%20the%20downward%20spiral%20of%20inequality%2C%20conflict%2C%20and%20ecological%20destruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELysa%20John%20is%20Secretary-General%20of%20CIVICUS%2C%20a%20global%20alliance%20working%20to%20strengthen%20citizen%20participation%20and%20defend%20civic%20freedoms.%20She%20has%20championed%20human%20rights%20and%20international%20mobilisation%20for%20over%2025%20years%2C%20starting%20her%20journey%20with%20grassroots%20organisations%20in%20India%20and%20subsequently%20spearheading%20trans-national%20campaigns%20for%20governance%20accountability.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709861447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07160635%2Falain-bonnardeaux-N_binrWZfD4-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2F2024-a-big-year-for-women-and-democracy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20India%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20national%20elections%20which%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year.%20Three%20other%20major%20democracies%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20join%20India%20as%20the%20big%20ones%20deciding%20their%20fates%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2F2024-a-big-year-for-women-and-democracy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20Warns%20Against%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BRevenge%2C%20Retribution%26quot%3B%20In%20High-Stakes%20Speech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20will%20use%20his%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address%20Thursday%20to%20attack%20election%20rival%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20plotting%20%26quot%3Brevenge%20and%20retribution%26quot%3B%20while%20offering%20skeptical%20voters%20his%20own%20optimistic%20version%20of%20an%20American%20comeback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20speeches%20of%20his%20long%20political%20career%2C%20the%2081-year-old%20Democrat%20will%20try%20to%20ease%20growing%20concerns%20among%20voters%20about%20his%20age%20by%20painting%20himself%20as%20the%20only%20alternative%20to%20to%20anti-democratic%20Trump%20in%20November's%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20lifetime%20has%20taught%20me%20to%20embrace%20freedom%20and%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20was%20to%20say%20in%20the%20primetime%20speech%20starting%20at%209%3A00%20pm%20(0200%20GMT)%2C%20according%20to%20excerpts%20released%20by%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20some%20other%20people%20my%20age%2C%20see%20a%20different%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20clear%20dig%20at%20Trump%2C%20although%20without%20mentioning%20his%20name.%20%26quot%3BAn%20American%20story%20of%20resentment%2C%20revenge%2C%20and%20retribution.%20That's%20not%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20oldest%20president%20in%20US%20history%2C%20Biden%20narrowly%20trails%20in%20the%20polls%20behind%20Republican%20former%20president%20Trump%2C%20who%20at%2077%20is%20just%20four%20years%20younger%20than%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20routinely%20paints%20Trump%20--%20who%20was%20impeached%20twice%20and%20faces%20multiple%20criminal%20indictments%20including%20for%20trying%20to%20overturn%20his%202020%20election%20loss%20--%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20survival%20of%20US%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20Biden%20was%20also%20to%20slam%20Republican%20abortion%20opponents%2C%20saying%20they%20have%20%26quot%3Bno%20clue%20about%20the%20power%20of%20women%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20what%20Democrats%20see%20as%20a%20key%20vote-winning%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20many%20Americans%20struggling%20from%20high%20prices%2C%20Biden%20was%20to%20say%20of%20the%20US%20economy%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20thousands%20of%20cities%20and%20towns%20the%20American%20people%20are%20writing%20the%20greatest%20comeback%20story%20never%20told.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20also%20set%20to%20use%20the%20annual%20speech%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20Congress%20to%20overcome%20doubts%20about%20US%20support%20for%20Israel's%20war%20on%20Hamas%2C%20and%20for%20Washington's%20backing%20for%20Ukraine%20against%20Russia's%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20to%20announce%20during%20the%20speech%20that%20he%20has%20ordered%20the%20US%20military%20to%20set%20up%20a%20port%20on%20Gaza's%20coast%20to%20bring%20in%20more%20aid%2C%20reflecting%20the%20acute%20political%20pressure%20from%20many%20in%20his%20own%20party%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiden's%20age%20under%20scrutiny%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20millions%20of%20Americans%20tuning%20in%20to%20the%20spectacle%20will%20be%20watching%20not%20just%20what%20Biden%20says%20in%20the%20joint%20session%20of%20Congress%2C%20but%20how%20he%20says%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20he%20stumble%2C%20for%20example%3F%20Or%20will%20he%20mix%20up%20the%20names%20of%20people%20and%20countries%2C%20deepening%20concerns%20fueled%20by%20a%20recent%20special%20counsel%20report%20that%20described%20him%20as%20elderly%20and%20forgetful%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20Biden%20was%20fully%20prepared%20for%20the%20speech%20--%20and%20ready%20for%20any%20repeat%20of%20last%20year's%20heckling%20by%20Trump%20allies%2C%20which%20he%20successfully%20parried%20with%20spirited%20ripostes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3