c-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20furniture%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20furniture%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20product%20packaging%20recommends%20the%20Lilly%20Brush%20Pro%20Pet%20Hair%20Tool%20Kit%20for%20use%20in%20cars%2C%20and%20it%20definitely%20removes%20pet%20hair%20from%20car%20seats%20and%20floor%20mats.%20But%20we%20consider%20this%20tool%20one%20of%20the%20best%20pet%20hair%20removers%20because%20it%20also%20does%20a%20great%20job%20removing%20pet%20hair%20from%20furniture%20and%20carpeted%20surfaces%20like%20cat%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20did%20a%20great%20job%20removing%20hard-to-see%20fur%20from%20the%20sofa%2C%20and%20the%20long-handled%20crevice%20tool%20does%20an%20excellent%20job%20cleaning%20corners%20and%20tricky%20surfaces%2C%20like%20narrow%20spaces%20between%20chair%20cushions%20and%20car%20seats.%20On%20a%20carpeted%20cat%20tree%2C%20it%20pulled%20up%20several%20months'%20worth%20of%20embedded%20cat%20hair%20with%20several%20good%20scrapes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20only%20took%20about%2020%20minutes%20to%20thoroughly%20clean%20the%20tree's%20three%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20image%20shows%20the%20Lilly%20Brush%20crevice%20tool%20on%20a%20cat%20tree%20beside%20the%20Lilly%20Brush%20fur%20remover%20on%20a%20clean%20sofa.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ea3219ce7f1785b2e7a3a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Raypole%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20tool%20didn't%20work%20as%20well%20on%20clothing%2C%20in%20part%20because%20of%20its%20broader%20shape%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20totally%20ineffective%2C%20either.%20We%20love%20the%20stretchy%20band%20that%20keeps%20the%20tool%20firmly%20in%20your%20hand%20as%20you%20use%20it.%20The%20Lilly%20Brush%20Pro%20Pet%20Hair%20Tool%20Kit%20costs%20more%20than%20nearly%20all%20of%20the%20other%20tools%20we%20tested%2C%20but%20it's%20effective%2C%20durable%2C%20and%20well-made%2C%20so%20we%20think%20it's%20worth%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20carpet%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20carpet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Neater%20Pets%20Fur%20Dozer%20Pet%20Hair%20Remover%20isn't%20the%20best%20option%20for%20pulling%20pet%20hair%20from%20clothing%2C%20but%20it%20really%20shines%20on%20carpet.%20We%20tried%20it%20on%20different%20types%20of%20carpet%2C%20furniture%2C%20and%20dog%20beds%20and%20found%20that%20it%20works%20best%20when%20it%20gets%20some%20resistance%20from%20the%20material%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20good%20option%20for%20rugged%20fabrics%2C%20like%20the%20dog%20bed%20pictured%2C%20and%20higher%20pile%20carpeting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Fur%20Dozer%20shown%20beside%20fur%20removed%20from%20a%20dog%20bed%20and%20also%20carpeting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ea429190413ab8e1da96ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Raypole%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20sturdy%20tool%20is%20made%20to%20last%2C%20and%20its%20small%20size%20means%20you%20can%20store%20it%20pretty%20much%20anywhere%2C%20including%20your%20bag%20or%20car.%20But%20even%20though%20the%20Fur%20Dozer%20is%20small%2C%20it's%20wide%20enough%20to%20quickly%20cover%20even%20larger%20surfaces%2C%20like%20area%20rugs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20liked%20how%20it's%20comfortable%20to%20hold%20or%20use%20with%20either%20hand%2C%20which%20means%20you%20can%20switch%20off%20hands%20for%20longer%20cleaning%20jobs.%20The%20quiet%20operation%20was%20another%20plus.%20Some%20pet%20hair%20removers%20make%20scratching%20or%20scraping%20sounds%20that%20can%20bother%20some%20sensitive%20or%20anxious%20dogs%2C%20but%20the%20Fur%20Dozer%20worked%20quietly%20enough%20that%20our%20pets%20didn't%20mind%20sticking%20around%20during%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20laundry%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20laundry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20wash%20a%20lot%20of%20fur-covered%20garments%2C%20blankets%2C%20and%20pet%20towels%2C%20the%20Smart%20Sheep%20Wool%20Dryer%20Balls%20can%20help%20your%20laundry%20come%20out%20of%20the%20dryer%20hair-free%20%E2%80%94%20and%20all%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20toss%20them%20in%20the%20dryer%20with%20the%20wet%20clothes.%20We%20loved%20how%20well%20they%20worked%20and%20cut%20down%20on%20drying%20time.%20A%20trip%20through%20the%20dryer%20with%20one%20of%20these%20balls%20got%20most%20of%20the%20cat%20hair%20off%20the%20curtain%20pictured%2C%20which%20is%20a%20favorite%20space%20for%20cat%20naps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Smart%20Sheep%20Wool%20Dryer%20Balls%20are%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20contain%20only%20wool%2C%20and%20don't%20have%20any%20fragrance.%20While%20they%20don't%20last%20forever%2C%20they%20do%20last%20a%20long%20time.%20The%20package%20directions%20say%20they'll%20still%20work%20once%20they%20begin%20pilling%2C%20but%20they%20removed%20a%20little%20less%20hair%20after%20drying%20more%20than%2015%20loads%2C%20especially%20loads%20of%20hairy%20items%20like%20dog%20blankets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20new%20and%20one%20used%20Smart%20Sheep%20dryer%20balls%20are%20shown%20beside%20the%20product%20directions.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ea3ed96080194819fdd6bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Raypole%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20dryer%20sheets%2C%20the%20balls%20don't%20do%20much%20to%20reduce%20static%20cling%2C%20but%20they're%20one%20of%20the%20best%20pet%20hair%20removers%20you%20can%20find%20for%20laundry.%20Plus%2C%20not%20only%20are%20they%20more%20effective%20than%20the%20dryer%20sheets%20we%20tested%2C%20they're%20better%20for%20your%20clothing%20and%20the%20environment.%20Just%20make%20sure%20to%20store%20them%20out%20of%20reach%20of%20your%20dog%2C%20since%20they%20can%20easily%20grab%20and%20shred%20any%20stray%20dryer%20balls%20that%20escape%20your%20laundry%20basket.%20(This%20happened%20during%20our%20trials!)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20car%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20car%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Analan%20Mini%20Pet%20Hair%20Detailer%20is%20a%20small%20tool%20that%20works%20best%20for%20removing%20pet%20hair%20from%20car%20seats%20and%20floor%20mats.%20The%20triangular%20tool%20has%20teeth%20running%20along%20its%20edges%20%E2%80%94%20three%20different%20sides%20with%20different%20tooth%20sizes.%20Starting%20with%20Side%201%2C%20which%20has%20the%20largest%20teeth%2C%20you%20work%20the%20tool%20over%20the%20cleaning%20area%2C%20using%20all%20of%20the%20sides%20to%20remove%20the%20hair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20loved%20how%20well%20it%20worked%20in%20the%20car%20and%20on%20furniture.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20found%20that%20most%20of%20the%20hair%20came%20up%20when%20we%20used%20the%20first%20side.%20We%20tried%20this%20on%20car%20seats%20and%20floor%20mats%2C%20dog%20beds%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20household%20furniture.%20It%20works%20best%20on%20carpeted%20or%20upholstered%20surfaces%2C%20like%20rugs%20and%20car%20seats%2C%20but%20it%20does%20an%20OK%20job%20removing%20pet%20hair%20from%20clothes%2C%20too.%20It's%20less%20effective%20on%20very%20shaggy%20fabrics%2C%20however.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20images%20show%20a%20fur-covered%20car%20seat%20beside%20a%20clean%20seat%20with%20the%20Analan%20Pet%20Hair%20Remover%20on%20top%20of%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ea338ece7f1785b2e7a44e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Raypole%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20tool's%20small%20size%20makes%20it%20very%20portable%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20easily%20stash%20it%20in%20a%20bag%20or%20car%20glovebox.%20The%20small%20size%20may%20be%20a%20drawback%20if%20you%20have%20larger%20hands%2C%20since%20you%20may%20find%20the%20tool%20harder%20to%20hold%20or%20manipulate.%20The%20size%20also%20makes%20it%20less%20ideal%20for%20very%20large%20surfaces%2C%20like%20floors%20or%20area%20rugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20roller%5C%22%3EBest%20roller%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20prefer%20a%20standard%20roller%2C%20the%20Scotch-Brite%20Pet%20Hair%20Pickup%20is%20a%20good%20option.%20It%20has%20super%20sticky%20sheets%20specially%20designed%20to%20pull%20pet%20hair%20from%20clothing%20and%20furniture.%20It%20worked%20on%20everything%20we%20tested%2C%20including%20a%20sweater%20that%20defeated%20some%20of%20the%20other%20best%20pet%20hair%20removers%2C%20and%20does%20a%20better%20job%20removing%20pet%20hair%20than%20many%20other%20sticky%20rollers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Scotch-Brite%20sticky%20roller%20is%20shown%20beside%20a%20sweater%20covered%20with%20fur%20and%20the%20same%20sweater%20with%20fur%20removed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ea3dc2ce7f1785b2e7a8ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Raypole%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20not%20perfect.%20The%20sheets%20spin%20loosely%20on%20the%20roller%2C%20making%20the%20tool%20less%20effective%20unless%20you%20grip%20it%20firmly%20and%20press%20down%20hard.%20This%20also%20makes%20it%20more%20difficult%20to%20tear%20off%20the%20sheets.%20We%20found%20that%20the%20roller%20would%20spin%20too%20far%20when%20we%20tried%20to%20tear%20off%20the%20used%20sheet%2C%20and%20the%20clean%20sheets%20would%20end%20up%20sticking%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20great%20choice%20for%20quick%20pet%20hair%20removal%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20want%20something%20to%20keep%20in%20your%20car%20or%20bag.%20However%2C%20we%20don't%20recommend%20it%20for%20large%20areas%20or%20deeply%20embedded%20pet%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20pet%20hair%20remover%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20things%20you'll%20want%20to%20consider%20when%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20pet%20hair%20removers%20will%20generally%20depend%20on%20what%20you%20want%20to%20use%20the%20tool%20for.%20A%20few%20things%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecommended%20surfaces%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENot%20all%20pet%20hair%20removers%20work%20the%20same%20way%2C%20and%20some%20do%20a%20better%20job%20on%20some%20surfaces%20than%20others.%20If%20you%20mostly%20need%20to%20remove%20pet%20hair%20from%20clothing%2C%20you%20may%20want%20a%20smaller%20tool%2C%20like%20a%20roller%20or%20sponge%2C%20that's%20designed%20for%20delicate%20fabrics.%20You%20may%20find%20a%20different%20tool%20works%20better%20for%20larger%2C%20carpeted%20surfaces%2C%20like%20your%20rug%20or%20sofa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShape%20and%20size%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you%20know%20you'll%20use%20the%20pet%20hair%20remover%20often%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20can%20hold%20it%20comfortably%20and%20use%20it%20easily.%20People%20with%20very%20small%20or%20very%20large%20hands%20may%20find%20certain%20tools%20harder%20to%20grip%20and%20use%20over%20a%20longer%20period.%20The%20shape%20of%20a%20tool%20can%20also%20affect%20how%20well%20it%20works%20for%20different%20surfaces%20and%20situations.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Chom%20Chom%20Roller%20has%20a%20larger%20size%20that%20makes%20it%20a%20little%20awkward%20to%20use%20on%20clothing%20you're%20already%20wearing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperation%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBefore%20purchasing%20a%20pet%20hair%20remover%2C%20read%20the%20directions%20and%20product%20reviews.%20This%20information%20can%20give%20you%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20how%20the%20tool%20works%20and%20whether%20people%20found%20it%20easy%20to%20use%20as%20directed.%20Most%20pet%20hair%20removers%20are%20fairly%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20but%20some%20may%20require%20more%20steps%20or%20cleaning%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20pet%20hair%20removers%2C%20you'll%20find%20plenty%20of%20options%20for%20different%20budgets.%20The%20prices%20of%20our%20top%20picks%20range%20from%20%245%20to%20%2433.%20While%20%2430%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20lot%20to%20spend%20upfront%2C%20a%20more%20expensive%20reusable%20tool%20may%20be%20worth%20the%20expense%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20go%20through%20single-use%20lint%20rollers%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20pet%20hair%20removers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20the%20best%20pet%20hair%20removers%20for%20all%20of%20your%20needs%2C%20we%20tested%2013%20tools%20across%20seven%20different%20categories.%20We%20scored%20each%20product%20in%20the%20following%20categories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEffectiveness%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20tested%20how%20well%20each%20tool%20worked%20when%20used%20for%20its%20intended%20purpose%20according%20to%20the%20product%20directions.%20We%20also%20checked%20how%20well%20the%20tool%20worked%20on%20additional%20surfaces%20not%20listed%20in%20the%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20effectiveness%2C%20we%20used%20each%20pet%20hair%20remover%20for%20both%20dog%20and%20cat%20hair%20on%20the%20following%20surfaces%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EClothing%20and%20bedding%20in%20several%20different%20fabrics%2C%20including%20T-shirts%2C%20jeans%2C%20sweatshirts%2C%20tights%2C%20sweaters%2C%20jackets%2C%20sheets%2C%20pillowcases%2C%20and%20duvet%20covers%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFurniture%2C%20including%20sofas%2C%20chairs%2C%20and%20cat%20trees%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFlooring%2C%20including%20high%20and%20low%20pile%20carpet%2C%20area%20rugs%2C%20tile%2C%20and%20concrete%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDog%20beds%2C%20including%20plush%2C%20shaggy%2C%20and%20carpeted%20beds%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECar%20floor%20mats%20and%20seats%2C%20though%20only%20some%20removers%20were%20tested%20on%20leather%20seats%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20pet%20hair%20removers%20designed%20for%20laundry%20by%20adding%20dryer%20sheets%20or%20dryer%20balls%20to%20wet%20clothes%20in%20the%20dryer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20used%20sticky%20single-use%20rollers%20on%20all%20of%20the%20testing%20surfaces%20listed%20above.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20each%20product%2C%20we%20evaluated%20the%20ease%20of%20operation%2C%20effort%20required%20to%20pick%20up%20pet%20hair%2C%20and%20effort%20required%20to%20clean%20the%20tool%20after%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20test%20durability%2C%20we%20used%20each%20pet%20hair%20remover%20daily%20on%20a%20few%20different%20surfaces%20over%20a%20period%20of%20two%20weeks.%20We%20used%20the%20dryer%20sheets%20and%20dryer%20balls%20in%2015%20loads%20of%20laundry%20containing%20a%20variety%20of%20fabrics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20evaluated%20whether%20anyone%20could%20comfortably%20use%20these%20tools%20or%20if%20they%20worked%20better%20for%20people%20with%20larger%20or%20smaller%20hands.%20We%20also%20considered%20whether%20the%20tool%20needed%20a%20very%20tight%20grip%20to%20work%20as%20intended.%20To%20check%20this%2C%20we%20had%20people%20with%20different%20hand%20sizes%20hold%20each%20tool%20and%20try%20using%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20checked%20prices%20for%20similar%20products%20to%20determine%20whether%20each%20tool%20had%20a%20comparable%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20functions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20tested%20other%20advertised%20functions%20of%20the%20product%2C%20like%20picking%20up%20leaf%20debris%20and%20dirt%20or%20reducing%20static%20cling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%20and%20storage%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20considered%20whether%20these%20pet%20hair%20removers%20were%20easy%20to%20take%20on%20the%20go%20or%20store%20at%20home%2C%20depending%20on%20their%20intended%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EPet%20hair%20remover%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20most%20effective%20pet%20hair%20remover%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20find%20plenty%20of%20different%20options%20when%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20pet%20hair%20removers%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20single%20most%20effective%20fur%20remover%20for%20all%20situations.%20The%20best%20tool%20for%20your%20needs%20can%20depend%20on%20the%20surface%20you%20want%20to%20use%20it%20on%2C%20how%20much%20hair%20you%20want%20to%20remove%2C%20and%20how%20often%20you%20need%20to%20use%20the%20tool.%20Our%20best%20overall%20pick%2C%20the%20Chom%20Chom%20Roller%2C%20was%20the%20most%20effective%20pet%20hair%20remover%20for%20the%20most%20surfaces%20and%20types%20of%20pet%20hair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20picks%20up%20dog%20hair%20the%20best%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20pet%20hair%20removers%20work%20well%20to%20pick%20up%20dog%20hair%2C%20including%20all%20of%20our%20top%20picks.%20You%20may%20need%20to%20try%20a%20few%20different%20tools%20to%20find%20the%20one%20that%20works%20best%20for%20your%20dog's%20fur.%20We%20particularly%20liked%20the%20Gonzo%20Natural%20Pet%20Hair%20Remover%20and%20the%20Fur%20Dozer%20for%20picking%20up%20dog%20hair%20embedded%20in%20furniture%20and%20carpet.%20However%2C%20some%20dog%20fur%20may%20prove%20extra%20resistant.%20If%20you%20don't%20get%20the%20results%20you%20want%20from%20a%20handheld%20pet%20hair%20remover%2C%20you