20realized%20the%20airline%20could%20be%20a%20great%20value%20on%20certain%20trips.%3Cp%3ECarly%20Caramanna%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20I%20was%20really%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20my%20experience%2C%20and%20I'd%20gladly%20fly%20Spirit%20again%20for%20a%20quick%20trip.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20arrived%20at%20my%20destination%20safely%20and%20cheaply.%20I%20liked%20that%20my%20%2418%20flight%20left%20me%20with%20more%20money%20to%20spend%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20trip.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20members%20I%20encountered%20were%20very%20friendly%20as%20well%2C%20further%20adding%20to%20my%20pleasant%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20flight%20was%20bare%20bones%2C%20I%20had%20no%20issue%20with%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20think%20Spirit%20flights%20can%20be%20a%20great%20value%20if%20you%20bring%20your%20own%20snacks%20and%20travel%20light%2C%20therefore%20avoiding%20additional%20baggage%20fees%20and%20extra%20food%20costs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20I%20were%20on%20a%20longer%20flight%2C%20I%20might%20consider%20paying%20extra%20(about%20%245)%20to%20choose%20an%20aisle%20seat%2C%20my%20preferred%20spot%20on%20a%20plane.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20although%20I%20had%20a%20good%20experience%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20wouldn't%20book%20Spirit%20for%20a%20super-important%20or%20time-sensitive%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpirit%20doesn't%20have%20as%20many%20routes%20as%20larger%20air%20carriers%2C%20so%20I'd%20be%20concerned%20about%20getting%20stuck%20in%20my%20departure%20city%20if%20my%20flight%20got%20canceled.%20If%20that%20happened%2C%20I'd%20probably%20have%20to%20fork%20over%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-day-to-book-flight-save-on-airfare-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elast-minute%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20another%20airline%2C%20defeating%20the%20purpose%20