rder%2C%20which%20took%20place%20in%20Haryana's%20Rohtak%2C%20has%20been%20claimed%20by%20Rohit%20Godara%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20who%20alleged%20in%20a%20video%20that%20the%20man%20who%20had%20been%20shot%20was%20a%20bookie%20and%20associated%20with%20their%20rivals%2C%20the%20Kaushal%20Chaudhary-Amit%20Dagar%20gang.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20alleged%20murderers%20had%20escaped%20from%20a%20reform%20home%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20were%20paid%20to%20kill%20the%20businessman.%20They%20were%20arrested%20from%20near%20the%20Nepal%20border%2C%20while%20trying%20to%20flee%2C%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMurder%20Footage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20scrap%20trader%2C%20identified%20as%20Sachin%2C%20was%20headed%20to%20Punjab's%20Sangrur%20with%20his%20mother%2C%20wife%20and%20children%20to%20attend%20a%20wedding.%20The%20family%20stopped%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Rohtak's%20Lakhan%20Majra%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20February%2029.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnCCTV%20footage%20shows%20Sachin%20walking%20out%20of%20the%20restaurant%20to%20his%20SUV%20and%2C%20as%20he%20nears%20it%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20one%20of%20his%20children%20enter%20the%20frame.%20A%20white%20car%20that%20had%20been%20waiting%20by%20the%20roadside%20drives%20towards%20the%20SUV%20and%20Sachin's%20unsuspecting%20wife%20asks%20her%20child%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20way.%20As%20the%20car%20stops%20near%20the%20SUV%2C%20the%20man's%20mother%20and%20the%20other%20child%2C%20a%20toddler%2C%20also%20come%20into%20view.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20wife%20can%20be%20heard%20shouting%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20they%20are%20looting%20him%26quot%3B.%20Two%20of%20the%20men%20then%20open%20fire%20at%20Sachin%2C%20who%20was%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat.%20While%20the%20wife%20takes%20the%20children%20to%20safety%2C%20the%20mother%20runs%20towards%20Sachin%20and%20the%20people%20shooting%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20firing%20a%20few%20rounds%2C%20the%20men%20head%20towards%20their%20car%20before%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20passenger's%20side%20of%20the%20SUV%20and%20opening%20fire%20again%2C%20pushing%20away%20Sachin's%20mother%2C%20who%20was%20trying%20to%20save%20him.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnEven%20as%20the%20mother%20keeps%20lamenting%2C%20%26quot%3Bmy%20child%20has%20been%20killed%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20men%20collect%20something%20from%20the%20SUV%20and%20leave%20in%20the%20waiting%20car.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20her%20complaint%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20mother%2C%20who%20suffered%20a%20bullet%20injury%20herself%2C%20said%20Sachin%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%20She%20said%20the%20attackers%20also%20took%20away%20his%20cellphone.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EGangster's%20Video%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20a%20video%20that%20is%20now%20going%20viral%2C%20a%20man%20claiming%20to%20be%20gangster%20Rohit%20Godara%2C%20who%20had%20also%20taken%20responsibility%20for%20killing%20Rashtriya%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%20chief%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%20in%20Jaipur%20in%20December%2C%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20Rohit%20Godara%20Goldy%20Brar%20(a%20reference%20to%20another%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20member).%20The%20bookie%20(Sachin%20Goda)%20of%20Gurugram%2C%20who%20considered%20himself%20the%20biggest%20bookie%20of%20Delhi%20has%20been%20killed%20in%20Lakhan%20Majra%2C%20Haryana.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20take%20full%20responsibility%20for%20this.%20He%20was%20a%20partner%20of%20our%20enemies%20Kaushal%20Chaudhary%20and%20Amit%20Dagar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20gangster%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20had%20made%20national%20headlines%20after%20it%20had%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%20in%202022.%20It%20is%20also%20said%20to%20have%20links%20with%20Khalistani%20outfits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Scrap%20And%20Property%20Dealer'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin's%20younger%20brother%2C%20Amit%2C%20said%20he%20was%20a%20scrap%20businessman.%20%26quot%3BMy%20mother%20was%20also%20shot%20in%20the%20leg.%20My%20brother%20was%20shot%2010-15%20times.%20He%20was%20a%20scrap%20dealer%20and%20property%20dealer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Rohit%20Godara%20claiming%20Sachin%20was%20a%20bookie%2C%20Amit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20knowledge%20of%20any%20such%20thing.%20We%20want%20justice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20childhood%20friend%2C%20Deepak%2C%20said%20Sachin%20had%20received%20threats%20recently.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20not%20linked%20to%20any%20gang%2C%20he%20was%20a%20scrap%20and%20property%20dealer.%20Three%20to%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20his%20partner%20was%20also%20killed%20after%20extortion%20attempts%2C%26quot%3B%20Deepak%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20official%20said%20the%20gang%20war%20angle%20is%20also%20being%20investigated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709839320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F9j4p5sv8_gurugram-trader-shot_625x300_08_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurugram-trader-shot-dead-in-front-of-mother-wife-and-children-5196734%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20daring%2C%20bone-chilling%20murder%20caught%20on%20camera%2C%20a%20scrap%20trader%20from%20Gurugram%20was%20killed%20after%20being%20shot%20multiple%20times%20by%20three%20men%20in%20front%20of%20his%20mother%2C%20wife%20and%20two%20little%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurugram-trader-shot-dead-in-front-of-mother-wife-and-children-5196734%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurugram-trader-shot-dead-in-front-of-mother-wife-and-c