2TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fimtiaz-ali-reveals-why-he-cast-diljit-dosanjh-and-parineeti-chopra-in-amar-singh-chamkila%2Farticleshow%2F108307061.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Every%20Citizen%20Has%20Right%20To%20Criticise%20Any%20Decision%20of%20State%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20upheld%20the%20right%20to%20dissent%2C%20saying%20every%20criticism%20is%20not%20an%20offence%20and%20if%20it%20were%20thought%20so%2C%20democracy%20would%20not%20survive.%20The%20police%20should%20be%20sensitised%20about%20freedom%20of%20speech%20granted%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20court%20added%2C%20throwing%20out%20a%20case%20against%20a%20man%20who%20had%20made%20adverse%20comments%20on%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20granted%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%2C%20guarantees%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%20Under%20the%20said%20guarantee%2C%20every%20citizen%20has%20the%20right%20to%20offer%20criticism%20of%20the%20action%20of%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20or%2C%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20every%20decision%20of%20the%20State.%20He%20has%20the%20right%20to%20say%20he%20is%20unhappy%20with%20any%20decision%20of%20the%20State%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20is%20the%20time%20to%20educate%20our%20police%20machinery%20about%20the%20concept%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20guaranteed%20by%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20limits%20of%20reasonable%20restraint%20on%20them%E2%80%A6%20They%20should%20be%20sensitized%20about%20the%20democratic%20values%20enshrined%20in%20our%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20criminal%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20Javed%20Ahmed%20Hazam%2C%20a%20Kashmiri%20professor%20working%20at%20Maharashtra's%20Kolhapur%20College%20for%20a%20WhatsApp%20status%20that%20called%20August%205%20a%20%26quot%3BBlack%20Day%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%26quot%3B%20and%20celebrated%20Pakistan's%20Independence%20Day%20on%20August%2014.%20The%20court%20ordered%20that%20the%20case%20against%20him%20be%20scrapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20calling%20August%205%20a%20%26quot%3BBlack%20day%26quot%3B%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bexpression%20of%20protest%20and%20pain%26quot%3B.%20Wishing%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20a%20happy%20Independence%20Day%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20goodwill%20gesture%20and%20cannot%20be%20said%20to%20create%20feelings%20of%20animosity%2C%20hostility%2C%20hatred%20or%20ill-will%20between%20different%20religious%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20test%20in%20such%20cases%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20the%20effect%20of%20the%20words%20on%20some%20weak-minded%20persons%20who%20see%20danger%20in%20every%20hostile%20approach%2C%20but%20the%20general%20effect%20of%20statements%20on%20reasonable%20persons%20who%20are%20significant%20in%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20because%20some%20individuals%20may%20develop%20hatred%20or%20ill%20will%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20sufficient%20to%20attract%20penalty%20for%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups%2C%20the%20court%20said.%20%26quot%3BLegal%20means%20should%20be%20considered%20a%20part%20of%20the%20right%20to%20live%20a%20dignified%20and%20meaningful%20life%20guaranteed%20by%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%20(which%20grants%20freedom%20of%20speech)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20caveat%20%E2%80%93%20the%20opposition%20or%20disagreement%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20within%20the%20four%20corners%20of%20the%20methods%20permitted%20in%20a%20democratic%20system%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709832780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fcq5c2cmg_supreme-court-reuters_625x300_06_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizens-have-right-to-criticise-scrapping-of-article-370-supreme-court-5195633%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20upheld%20the%20right%20to%20dissent%2C%20saying%20every%20criticism%20is%20not%20an%20offence%20and%20if%20it%20were%20thought%20so%2C%20democracy%20would%20not%20survive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizens-have-right-to-criticise-scrapping-of-article-370-supreme-court-5195633%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizens-have-right-to-criticise-scrapping-of-article-370-supreme-court-5195633%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizens-have-right-to-criticise-scrapping-of-article-370-supreme-court-5195633%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sebi%20bars%20JM%20Financial%20from%20acting%20as%20lead%20manager%20of%20debt%20issue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709832780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F13%2Ffull%2F1697213648-3949.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Finvestment%2Fsebi-bars-jm-financial-from-acting-as-lead-manager-for-public-debt-issue-124030701087_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shares%20of%20JM%20Financial%20tanked%20by%2020%20per%20cent%20following%20the%20RBI%20order%20on%20Wednesday.%20Later%2C%20the%20stock%20recouped%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20losses%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww