top%2010%20standalone%20autocratizers%20in%202023%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fv-dem.net%2F%5C%22%3Ereport.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20says%20that%20India%20dropped%20down%20to%20electoral%20autocracy%20in%202018%20and%20remains%20in%20this%20category%20by%20the%20end%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEight%20out%20of%20ten%20countries%20in%20this%20group%20were%20democracies%20before%20the%20start%20of%20autocratization.%20Democracy%20broke%20down%20in%20six%20of%20those%20eight%20cases%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Comoros%2C%20Hungary%2C%20India%2C%20Mauritius%2C%20Nicaragua%2C%20and%20Serbia.%20Only%20Greece%20and%20Poland%20remain%20democracies%20in%202023.%20This%20frequency%20of%20democratic%20breakdown%20matches%20with%20a%20recent%20study%20showing%20that%2080%25%20of%20democracies%20break%20down%20if%20they%20start%20autocratizing%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20report%20titled%20%E2%80%98Democracy%20Winning%20and%20Losing%20at%20the%20Ballot%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20autocratization%20process%20has%20been%20well%20documented%2C%20including%20gradual%20but%20substantial%20deterioration%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20compromising%20independence%20of%20the%20media%2C%20crackdowns%20on%20social%20media%2C%20harassment%20of%20journalists%20critical%20of%20the%20government%2C%20as%20well%20as%20attacks%20on%20civil%20society%20and%20intimidation%20of%20the%20opposition.%20The%20ruling%20anti-pluralist%2C%20Hindu-nationalist%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20at%20the%20helm%20has%20for%20example%20used%20laws%20on%20sedition%2C%20defamation%2C%20and%20counterterrorism%20to%20silence%20critics.%20The%20BJP%20government%20undermined%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20secularism%20by%20amending%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20in%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Modi-led%20government%20also%20continues%20to%20suppress%20the%20freedom%20of%20religion%20rights.%20Intimidation%20of%20political%20opponents%20and%20people%20protesting%20government%20policies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20silencing%20of%20dissent%20in%20academia%20are%20now%20prevalent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709830794000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18121214%2FGDpRC6VakAAZMy8.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsince-2018-india-has-remained-an-electoral-autocracy-v-dem-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20also%20lists%20in%20the%20top%2010%20standalone%20autocratizers%20in%202023%2C%20per%20the%20report%20titled%20'Democracy%20Winning%20and%20Losing%20at%20the%20Ballot'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsince-2018-india-has-remained-an-electoral-autocracy-v-dem-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20Busts%20Ring%20Trafficking%20Indians%20To%20Russia%2C%20Conducts%20Raids%20In%207%20Cities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20it%20emerged%20that%20a%20Hyderabad%20man%20duped%20into%20joining%20Russia's%20war%20against%20Ukraine%20has%20been%20killed%2C%20the%20CBI%20on%20Thursday%20busted%20a%20ring%20involved%20in%20trafficking%20Indians%20to%20the%20country%2C%20officials%20said.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20two%20dozen%20Indians%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20forced%20into%20fighting%20Russia's%20war%20after%20being%20tricked%20into%20going%20to%20the%20country%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20getting%20high-paying%20jobs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20agency%20registered%20a%20case%20and%20began%20carrying%20out%20raids%20at%20over%2010%20locations%20in%20seven%20cities%20associated%20with%20the%20agents%20and%20firms%20involved%20in%20the%20trafficking.%20The%20raids%20are%20being%20conducted%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20Ambala%2C%20Chandigarh%20and%20Madurai%2C%20and%20some%20suspects%20have%20been%20detained%20for%20questioning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20raids%2C%20it%20has%20emerged%20that%20the%20number%20of%20Indians%20sent%20by%20these%20firms%20to%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20is%2035.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20clear%20whether%20all%20of%20them%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI's%20case%20also%20names%20Dubai-based%20Faisal%20Khan%20alias%20Baba%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20YouTube%20channel%20Baba%20Vlogs.%20Khan's%20name%20has%20cropped%20up%20repeatedly%20in%20NDTV's%20conversations%20with%20families%20whose%20sons%20were%20taken%20to%20Russia%20and%20then%20forced%20into%20the%20country's%20war%20effort%20after%20being%20promised%20jobs%20as%20security%20guards%20or%20labourers%2C%20but%20with%20high%20wages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Khan's%20firm%2C%20Baba%20Vlogs%20Overseas%20Recruitment%20Solutions%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20three%20other%20companies%20have%20been%20named%20-%20one%20each%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Chandigarh.%20The%20directors%20of%20the%20companies%20are%20also%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20but%20it%20is%20not%20yet%20clear%20whether%20they%20or%20their%20companies%20were%20working%20with%20Khan%20or%20operating%20independently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20incriminating%20documents%2C%20electronic%20devices%20like%20desktops%2C%20laptops%20and%20phones%2C%20and%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20in%20cash%20have%20been%20seized%20in%20the%20raids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709830680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Ft1pbc4jo_wagner-group-reuters-650_625x300_24_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-raids-against-visa-agents-firms-in-7-cities-on-a