try's%20entry%20into%20NATO%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvictory%20for%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20turned%20the%20page%20on%20two%20centuries%20of%20non-alignment%20following%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accession%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20victory%20for%20freedom%20today.%20Sweden%20has%20made%20a%20free%2C%20democratic%2C%20sovereign%20and%20united%20choice%20to%20join%20NATO%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20ceremony%20in%20Washington%20with%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20historic%20day.%20Sweden%20will%20now%20take%20its%20rightful%20place%20at%20NATO's%20table%2C%20with%20an%20equal%20say%20in%20shaping%20NATO%20policies%20and%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20NATO%20Secretary-General%20Jens%20Stoltenberg%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20over%20200%20years%20of%20non-alignment%20Sweden%20now%20enjoys%20the%20protection%20granted%20under%20Article%205%2C%20the%20ultimate%20guarantee%20of%20allies'%20freedom%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Swedish%20government%20announced%20it%20was%20holding%20a%20special%20government%20meeting%20to%20approve%20accession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Swedish%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20to%20attend%20the%20annual%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address%20by%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20has%20been%20struggling%20to%20persuade%20the%20rival%20Republican%20Party%20to%20approve%20new%20aid%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESweden's%20blue%20and%20golden-yellow%20flag%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20hoisted%20on%20Monday%20at%20the%20Brussels%20headquarters%20of%20the%20North%20Atlantic%20Treaty%20Alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20vowed%20%26quot%3Bcountermeasures%26quot%3B%20over%20Sweden's%20entry%20into%20NATO%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20alliance's%20troops%20and%20assets%20deploy%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESweden%20and%20Finland%2C%20while%20both%20militarily%20intertwined%20with%20the%20United%20States%20and%20members%20of%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20have%20historically%20steered%20clear%20of%20officially%20joining%20NATO%2C%20formed%20in%20the%20Cold%20War%20to%20unite%20against%20the%20Soviet%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Finland%20joined%20last%20year%2C%20Sweden's%20membership%20means%20all%20the%20countries%20surrounding%20the%20Baltic%20Sea%2C%20except%20Russia%2C%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20US-led%20military%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20has%20led%20some%20to%20label%20the%20sea%20a%20%26quot%3BNATO%20lake%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20the%20Western%20allies%20now%20appearing%20well-placed%20to%20strangle%20Russia's%20room%20for%20manoeuvre%20in%20the%20crucial%20shipping%20route%20if%20a%20war%20with%20Moscow%20ever%20breaks%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Turning%20page%20on%20non-alignment%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESweden%20has%20not%20been%20involved%20in%20a%20war%2C%20including%20World%20War%20II%2C%20since%20the%20Napoleonic%20conflicts%20of%20the%20early%2019th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Finland%20and%20Sweden%20launched%20a%20joint%20bid%20after%20Russia%20in%202022%20invaded%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20had%20unsuccessfully%20sought%20to%20join%20NATO%20--%20which%20considers%20an%20attack%20on%20one%20member%20an%20attack%20on%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinland%20successfully%20joined%20in%20April%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESweden's%20candidacy%20stalled%20due%20to%20an%20assertive%20push%20by%20Turkey%2C%20which%20demanded%20that%20Stockholm%2C%20known%20for%20its%20liberal%20asylum%20policies%2C%20crack%20down%20on%20Kurdish%20militants%20who%20have%20campaigned%20against%20Ankara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurkish%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20later%20demanded%20action%20after%20protesters%2C%20enjoying%20Swedish%20laws%20on%20free%20speech%2C%20desecrated%20Islam's%20holy%20book%20the%20Koran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20clear%20if%20unstated%20sweetener%2C%20the%20United%20States%20dangled%20the%20prospect%20of%20F-16%20warplanes%20to%20Turkey%2C%20which%20has%20faced%20the%20wrath%20of%20US%20sanctions%20over%20a%20major%20military%20purchase%20from%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20in%20January%20approved%20%2423%20billion%20in%20F-16%20warplanes%20to%20Turkey%20swiftly%20after%20it%20ratified%20Sweden's%20membership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20simultaneously%20pushed%20ahead%20with%20%248.6%20billion%20in%20more%20advanced%20F-35%20jets%20for%20Greece%2C%20a%20fellow%20NATO%20member%20that%20has%20a%20historic%20rivalry%20and%20frequent%20tensions%20with%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20Turkey's%20blessing%2C%20Sweden%20faced%20another%20obstacle%20as%20it%20needed%20approval%20of%20a%20last%20country%20--%20Hungary%2C%20whose%20nationalist%20prime%20minister%2C%20Viktor%20Orban%2C%20has%20often%20thumbed%20his%20nose%20at%20Western%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hungarian%20parliament%20ratified%20Sweden's%20membership%20on%20February%2026.%20But%20in%20one%20last%20hiccup%2C%20Hungary%20could%20not%20formally%20sign%20the%20accession%20document%20due%20to%20a%20brief%20absence%20in%20the%20mostly%20ceremonial%20post%20of%20president%2C%20after%20an%20Orban%20ally%20resigned%20in%20a%20scandal%20over%20pardoning%20a%20convicted%20child%20abuser's%20accomplice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20poll%20by%20Swedish%20broadcaster%20SR%20said%20that%20most%20Swedes%20believe%20the%20country%20made%20too%20many%20sacrifices%20to%20join%20NATO%2C%20although%20more%20than%20three-quarters%20believed%20NATO%20would%20strengthen%20the%20country's%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709830380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fa2jurvvg_sweden-nato-_625x300_26_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-two-year-wait-sweden-joi