rs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BBrahMos%20Is%20Modern%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20used%20the%20Onyx%2C%20anti-ship%20supersonic%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20against%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20Kyiv%20reportedly%20claimed%20was%20intercepted%20and%20can%20be%20shot%20down.%20The%20extensive%20use%20of%20air%20defence%20systems%20and%20drones%20in%20the%20war%20has%20led%20to%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20BrahMos%20is%20undefeatable%20in%20the%20new-age%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Dinkar%2C%20Director-General%20at%20DRDO%20and%20the%20CEO%20of%20BrahMos%20Aerospace%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20think%20the%20Onyx%20missile%20and%20BrahMos%20are%20similar%20but%20let%20me%20be%20clear%20that%20they%20are%20not.%20Onyx%20is%20a%20dinosaur%20and%20BrahMos%20is%20a%20modern%20missile%20we%20believe%20that%20in%20the%20current%20context%20of%20warfare%2C%20it%20can%20hit%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20targets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fr52kfhio_brahmos-missile_625x300_14_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20with%20an%20anti-ship%20missile%20and%20as%20requirements%20changed%2C%20BrahMos%20evolved%20into%20different%20variants%20not%20just%20by%20anti-ship%20attacks%20but%20also%20by%20ship-launched%20land%20attacks.%26quot%3B%20BrahMos%20is%20the%20world's%20fastest%20supersonic%20cruise%20missile%20powered%20by%20its%20liquid%20ramjet%20engine.%20Mr%20Dinkar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20took%20several%20years%20for%20the%20Russians%20to%20build%20a%20liquid%20ramjet%20engine%2C%20which%20they%20shared%20with%20us%20and%20I%20have%20to%20tell%20you%20it's%20a%20piece%20of%20art.%26quot%3B%20On%20the%20induction%20of%20BrahMos%20in%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%2C%20Mr%20Dinkar%20said%20the%20blueprints%20are%20ready%20and%20we%20are%20raising%20funds%20and%20we%20are%20hopeful%20that%20by%202026%20it%20will%20be%20inducted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BrahMos%20missile%20can%20reach%20up%20to%20speeds%20of%20Mach%202.8%20(2.8%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20sound)%2C%20perform%20manoeuvres%20to%20evade%20air%20defence%20and%20be%20launched%20from%20land%2C%20sea%2C%20air%20and%20underwater.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFuture%20Of%20Tanks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russia-Ukraine%20War%20and%20Israel's%20ongoing%20offensive%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20witnessed%20the%20use%20of%20tanks.%20Still%2C%20the%20attacks%20against%20the%20heavy%20machinery%20by%20drones%2C%20landmines%20and%20even%20Molotovs%2C%20direct%20the%20focus%20on%20whether%20they%20are%20redundant%20in%20modern%20wars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20a%20column%20of%20tanks%20on%20a%20highway%20was%20sitting%20ducks%20for%20drones%2C%20molotovs%20and%20Ukrainian%20air%20attacks.%20Israel's%20Merkava%20tank%20was%20attacked%20by%20a%20drone-dropped%20grenade%2C%20damaging%20its%20turret%20and%20rendering%20it%20useless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F0f7kh32g_israeli-tanks-1200_625x300_08_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELt%20General%20Amit%20Sharma%20(Retired)%2C%20former%20chief%20of%20India's%20nuclear%20command%2C%20differed%20from%20the%20view%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTank%20is%20the%20only%20piece%20of%20equipment%20that%20will%20enable%20the%20infantry%20to%20move%20and%20capture%20the%20objective.%20Tanks%20provide%20staying%20part%20to%20the%20enemy%20to%20defend%20it.%20What%20we%20saw%20in%20Russia%20was%20poor%20training.%20Capture%20and%20defence%20of%20ground%20is%20important.%20Weapon%20systems%20have%20to%20change%2C%20and%20warfare%20has%20changed%20too.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanks%20move%20in%20a%20combined%20group%20where%20Infantry%2C%20Mechanized%20Infantry%2C%20close%20air%20support%20from%20helicopters%20and%20fighter%20jets%2C%20and%20engineers%20move%20in%20tandem%20as%20a%20battle%20group.%20In%20Russia%2C%20tanks%20had%20no%20support%2C%20they%20were%20sitting%20ducks%20for%20the%20enemy%2C%20Lt%20General%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turret%20of%20the%20tank%2C%20especially%20the%20T-90s%2C%20which%20are%20used%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%20too%2C%20is%20vulnerable%20to%20attacks.%20The%20'Jack-in-the-box'%20design%20where%20ammunition%20is%20stored%20near%20the%20turret%20exposes%20it%20to%20aerial%20attacks.%20In%20Russia%2C%20a%20%26quot%3BKamikaze%26quot%3B%20drone%20launched%20by%20Ukraine%20would%20attack%20the%20turret%20and%20blow%20the%20tank%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Armenia-Azerbaijan%20war%20in%202020%20saw%20an%20innovative%20way%20to%20counter%20such%20attacks.%20'Cope-Cages'%20or%20metal%20grills%20were%20attached%20on%20top%20of%20turrets%20to%20reduce%20the%20impact%20of%20such%20attacks.%20T-90%20Bhishmas%2C%20which%20are%20deployed%20in%20Ladakh%20have%20installed%20such%20cope-cages.%20Even%20Israeli%20Merkava%20tanks%20in%20Gaza%20have%20such%20systems%20after%20taking%20lessons%20from%20the%20Ukraine-Russia%20War.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrones%20-%20Cheap%20Way%20To%20Stay%20In%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthi%20rebels%20in%20Yemen%20have%20used%20drones%20to%20carry%20out%20attacks%20on%20merchant%20ships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20they%20say%20%26quot%3BIt's%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%26quot%3B.%20The%20attacks%20have%20affected%20global%20trade%20and%20India%2C%20which%20considers%20the%20Red%20Sea%20a%20primary%20area%20of%20importance%20in%20its%20maritim