-threats-what-experts-say-5195098%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fis-india-ready-to-face-emerging-threats-what-experts-say-5195098%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20Article%20370%20Was%20So%20Bad...%26quot%3B%3A%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20Slams%20PM%20Modi's%20Remarks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFarooq%20Abdullah%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20took%20strong%20exception%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20remarks%20today%20on%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20that%20it%20had%20only%20helped%20propagate%20dynastic%20rule%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Article%20370%20was%20this%20bad%2C%20how%20did%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20ever%20make%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20in%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20Srinagar%20today%20since%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20had%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%26quot%3B%20that%20was%20the%20result%20of%20the%20scrapping%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state's%20special%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20decades%2C%20for%20political%20gains%2C%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20misled%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Article%20370.%20But%20today%20there%20are%20equal%20rights%20and%20opportunities%20for%20all.%20The%20people%20know%20the%20truth...%20they%20were%20misled...%20This%20is%20the%20new%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20which%20we%20all%20were%20waiting%2C'%20he%20had%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20--%20a%20three-time%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20--%20hit%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Article%20370%20was%20this%20bad%20--%20I%20would%20like%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20re-hear%20the%20speech%20made%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20then%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%2C%20in%20which%20he%20compared%20two%2