35%2Fimage-1920.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20has%20deleted%20electoral%20bond-related%20documents%20from%20its%20website.%20This%20development%20surfaces%20amidst%20the%20bank%20seeking%20time%20till%20June%2030%20to%20submit%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20encashed%20by%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20links%20or%20webpages%20which%20don%E2%80%99t%20exist%20in%20the%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20website%20are%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fretail.onlinesbi.sbi%2Fdocuments%2FOperating_Guidelines_for_Donors.pdf%5C%22%3EOperating%20guidelines%20for%20donors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fretail.onlinesbi.sbi%2Fdocuments%2FFAQs.pdf%5C%22%3EFrequently%20Asked%20Questions%2FFAQs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20titled%20%E2%80%9COperating%20guidelines%20for%20donors%E2%80%9D%20was%20a%20gazette%20notification%20which%20was%20released%20on%20January%202%2C%202018.%20It%20listed%20basic%20information%20like%20who%20could%20purchase%20an%20electoral%20bond%2C%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20available%20in%20what%20denominations%2C%20what%20were%20the%20documents%20required%20to%20purchase%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20how%20to%20purchase%20(through%20NEFT%2C%20online%20transaction%2C%20etc.)%20and%20which%20are%20the%20SBI%20branches%20authorised%20for%20the%20purchase%20of%20the%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20FAQs%2C%20SBI%20had%20provided%20basic%20information%20related%20to%20electoral%20bonds%20like%20KYC%20requirements%20and%20citizenship%20proof%20required%20for%20the%20purchase%20of%20bonds%2C%20etc.%20The%20deleted%20documents%20were%20shared%20by%20senior%20journalist%20Nitin%20Sethi%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20(previously%20called%20Twitter)%20and%20another%20social%20media%20user%20%40indian_nagrik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAll%20the%20PDFs%20related%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FElectoralBonds%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ElectoralBonds%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20removed%20from%20the%20SBI%20website.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheOfficialSBI%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40TheOfficialSBI%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20come%20up%20with%20an%20explanation.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0cAEwsG2Hy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F0cAEwsG2Hy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Kapil%20(%40kapsology)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkapsology%2Fstatus%2F1765671020512399712%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%207%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhen-the-govt-wanted-electoral-bonds-data-sbi-didnt-need-extra-time-to-provide-it%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20Govt%20Wanted%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Data%2C%20SBI%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Need%20Extra%20Time%20to%20Provide%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20ordered%20the%20largest%20government-owned%20bank%20to%20release%20details%20of%20all%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20purchased%20by%20March%206.%20In%20total%2C%20including%20the%20latest%20tranche%2C%20Rs%2016%2C518.11%20crore%20electoral%20bonds%20have%20been%20sold%20by%20the%20SBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reporters-collective.in%2Fblog%2Fsbi-electoral-bonds-data%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Reporter%E2%80%99s%20Collective%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20SBI%20has%20provided%20crucial%20data%20related%20to%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20the%20finance%20ministry%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20sometimes%20even%20within%2048%20hours%20which%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20buy%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20argument%20that%20it%20will%20take%20months%20for%20it%20to%20match%20the%20buyer%20of%20the%20bonds%20with%20beneficiary%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20documents%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Reporter%E2%80%99s%20Collective%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Esuggests%20that%20the%20SBI%20collected%20data%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20from%20across%20the%20country%20within%2048%20hours%20after%20the%20deadline%20to%20encash%20the%20bonds%20ended%20and%20provided%20the%20information%20to%20the%20finance%20ministry.%20The%20report%20added%20that%20the%20bank%20shared%20such%20information%20religiously%20with%20the%20ministry%20after%20every%20window%20period%20of%20sale.%20The%20independent%20media%20platform%20has%20verified%20such%20missives%20being%20sent%20up%20to%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20report%20pointed%20out%20that%20electoral%20bond-related%20work%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20from%20printing%20to%20redemption%20%E2%80%93%20was%20overseen%20by%20a%20specific%20team%20of%20the%20SBI%20which%20was%20earlier%20called%20Transaction%20Banking%20Unit%20(TBU).%20This%20team%20collated%20information%20for%20the%20government%20at%20a%20short%20notice%20and%20kept%20the%20finance%20ministry%20officials%20informed%20about%20the%20trends%20in%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709826858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07212335%2Fimage-1920.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fnow-sbi-deletes-documents-related-to-electoral-bonds-from-website%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20document%20titled%20%26quot%3BOperating%20guidelines%20for%20donors%26quot%3B%20listed%20basic%20information%20like%20who%20could%20purchase%20an%20electoral%20bond%2C%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20available%20in%20what%20denominations%2C%20what%20were%20the%20documents%20required%20to%20purchase%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20etc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F