Cp%3EAiming%20to%20set%20up%20a%20holistic%20ecosystem%20for%20the%20development%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20on%20Thursday%20approved%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20an%20AI%20Mission%20with%20an%20outlay%20of%20over%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20of%20the%20mission%20will%20be%20to%20develop%20an%20end-to-end%20structure%20starting%20with%20the%20education%20of%20youngsters%20in%20the%20emerging%20field%20to%20setting%20up%20innovation%20centres%20and%20creating%20compute%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20Cabinet%20decisions%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20said%20the%20mission%20is%20in%20line%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20vision%20of%20democratising%20technology%20and%20making%20it%20available%20to%20every%20citizen%2C%20and%20that%20a%20capital%20outlay%20of%20Rs%2010%2C372%20crore%20has%20been%20approved%20for%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20out%20seven%20pillars%20of%20the%20mission%2C%20an%20official%20release%20said%20public%20and%20private%20sectors%20will%20collaborate%20to%20create%20a%20compute%20capacity%20of%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20graphics%20processing%20units%20(GPUs)%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20startups%20and%20promote%20research%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20innovation%20centres%20will%20also%20be%20set%20up%20to%20develop%20Large%20Multimodal%20Models%20which%20can%20work%20with%20multiple%20data%20types%20and%20help%20in%20key%20sectors%20like%20agriculture%20and%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20education%20and%20talent%2C%20the%20release%20said%20India%20ranks%20first%20in%20terms%20of%20AI%20skill%20penetration%20and%20access%20will%20be%20facilitated%20to%20courses%20in%20the%20sector%20at%20the%20undergraduate%2C%20postgraduate%20and%20PhD%20levels.%20In%20tier%202%20and%203%20cities%2C%20200%20AI%20and%20data%20labs%20will%20be%20set%20up%20to%20impart%20foundational-level%20courses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20other%20pillars%20are%20facilitating%20access%20to%20datasets%20and%20ensuring%20the%20responsible%20development%20of%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcoming%20the%20move%2C%20Minister%20Of%20State%20for%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%2C%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20said%20the%20mission%20will%20catalyse%20India's%20AI%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20poised%20to%20be%20the%20kinetic%20enabler%20for%20India's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDigitalEconomy%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DigitalEconomy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%9C%85%20PM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20has%20consistently%20emphasized%20that%20India%20is%20going%20to%20fully%20exploit%20the%20power%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAI%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20its%20citizens%20and%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20its%20economy.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%9C%85%20I%20am%20grateful%20to%20the%20Hon'ble%20PM%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjOWgZMyog7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FjOWgZMyog7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3(Modiyude%20Kutumbam)%20(%40Rajeev_GoI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRajeev_GoI%2Fstatus%2F1765743313251131791%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%207%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20minister%20also%20said%20the%20programme%20will%20position%20India%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cforce%20shaping%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20for%20India%20and%20for%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709825160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fj4lbd4g_artificial-intelligence_625x300_01_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-cabinet-approves-ai-mission-with-capital-outlay-of-rs-10-372-crore-5195204%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aiming%20to%20set%20up%20a%20holistic%20ecosystem%20for%20the%20development%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20on%20Thursday%20approved%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20an%20AI%20Mission%20with%20an%20outlay%20of%20over%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-cabinet-approves-ai-mission-with-capital-outlay-of-rs-10-372-crore-5195204%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-cabinet-approves-ai-mission-with-capital-outlay-of-rs-10-372-crore-5195204%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-cabinet-approves-ai-mission-with-capital-outlay-of-rs-10-372-crore-5195204%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20'Ghee'%20A%20Livestock%20Product%20Or%20Not%3F%20Supreme%20Court%20Said%20This%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20intriguing%20question%20came%20up%20during%20a%20hearing%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20-%20was%20'ghee'%20(clarified%20butter)%20a%20livestock%20product%20or%20not%3F%20The%20petitioner%20had%20argued%20that%20'ghee'%20is%20not%20a%20product%20of%20livestock%20as%20cows%20and%20buffaloes%20do%20not%20yield%20it%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%20that%20'ghee'%20is%20indeed%20a%20livestock%20product%20and%20the%20argument%20against%20it%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20stemmed%20from%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government's%201994%20notification%2C%20which%20grants%20market%20committees%20the%20authority%20to%20levy%20fees%20on%20its%20sale%20and%20purchase.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20tasked%20with%20determining%20whether%20'ghee'%20-%20a%20staple%20ingredient%20in%20Indian%20cuisine%20-%20qualifies%20as%20a%20livestock%20product%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(Agricultural%20Produce%20and%20Livestock)%20Markets%20Act%2C%201966.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%201994%20notification%20was%20met%20with%20resistance%20from%20producers%20of%20livestock%20products%20who%20challenged%20its%20validity%20in%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20High%20Court.%20They%20contended%20that%20ghee%20cannot%20be%20considered%20a%20product%20of%20livestock%20and%20therefore%20should%20not%20be%20subject%20to%20regulation%20and%20classification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20the%20contention%20and%20asserted%20that%20all%20livestock%20products%20fall%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Livestock%20Products%20Act%2C%20as%20defined%20by%20the%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20eventually%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20where%20two%20key%20questions%20were%20raised%3A%20whether%20ghee%20qualifies%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blivestock%20product%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%201966%20Act%20and%20whether%20the%20notification%20adhered%20to%20the%20prescribed%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%205%2C%20Justices%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20and%20SV%20Bhatti%20delivered%20a%20unanimous%20verdict%2C%20affirming%20ghee%20as%20a%20byproduct%20of%20milk%2C%20which%20unequivocally%20qualifies%20it%20as%20a%20livestock%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20acknowledged%20the%20High%20Court%20rightly%20held%20that%20even%20though%20'ghee'%20is%20not%20directly%20obtained%20from%20milk%2C%20which%20is%20a%20product%20of%20livestock%2C%20it%20would%20still%20be%20a%20'product%20of%20a%20product%20of%20livestock'%20and%20that%20it%20serves%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20legislation%20and%20payment%20of%20market%20fees%20related%20to%20livestock%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20inclusion%20of%20'ghee'%20as%20a%20livestock%20product%20cannot%20be%20faulted%20merely%20because%20it%20is%20derived%20from%20another%20dairy%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20dismissed%20the%20plea%20filed%20by%20Sangam%20Milk%20Producer%20Company%20Ltd%20against%20an%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20judgement%2C%20clearing%20the%20decks%20for%20the%20imposition%20of%20a%20fee%20on%20its%20sale%20and%20purchase%20through%20market%20committees%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20appeals%20dismissed%2C%20the%20Court%20rescinded%20earlier%20interim%20orders%2C%20allowing%20market%20committees%20to%20collect%20fees%20from%20appellants%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20High%20Court's%20decision.%20Recognizing%20the%20prolonged%20delay%20in%20fee%20payments%2C%20the%20Court%20granted%20appellants%20a%20two-year%20period%20to%20settle%20the%20dues%20in%20four%20equal%20installments.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709824620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fu21tgj88_ghee_625x300_03_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fis-ghee-a-livestock-product-or-not-supreme-court-said-this-5195456%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20intriguing%20question%20came%20up%20during%20a%20hearing%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20-%20was%20'ghee'%20(clarified%20butter)%20a%20livestock%20product%20or%20not%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fis-ghee-a-livestock-product-or-not-supreme-court-said-this-5195456%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fis-ghee-a-livestock-product-or-not-supreme-court-said-this-5195456%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fis-ghee-a-livestock-product-or-not-supreme-court-said-this-5195456%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Man%20Stabbed%20To%20Death%20Hours%20Before%20Wedding%2C%20Cops%20Suspect%20Father%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2029-year-old%20gym%20trainer%20was%20stabbed%2015%20times%20in%20his%20face%20and%20chest%20at%20his%20south%20Delhi%20home%20early%20today%2C%20just%20hours%20before%20his%20wedding.%20The%20police%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20man's%20father%2C%20the%20main%20suspect%20in%20the%20murder.%C2%A0The%20incident%20occurred%20in%20south%20Delhi's%20Devli%20Extension%20area%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20younger%20brother%20of%20Gaurav%20Singhal%2C%20the%20victim%2C%20and%20a%20relative%20have%20been%20detained%20for%20questioning%2C%20they%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20angles%20are%20being%20looked%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20motive%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20found.%20So%20far%2C%20we%20have%20come%20to%20know%20that%20there%20was%20some%20dispute%20between%20the%20man%20and%20his%20father.%20Everything%20will%20be%20clear%20after%20the%20main%20accused%20is%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(south)%20Ankit%20Chauhan%20said%20the%20police%20received%20a%20call%20about%20the%20incident%20around%2012%3A30%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20attack%2C%20Mr%20Singhal's%20family%20rushed%20him%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20declared%20dead%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGaurav%20Singhal's%20wedding%20was%20scheduled%20for%20today...%20It%20was%20an%20arranged%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DCP%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20shifted%20the%20body%20to%20the%20AIIMS%20mortuary%20for%20an%20autopsy%20and%20legal%20proceedings%20have%20been%20initiated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhal's%20family%2C%20however%2C%20said%20they%20do%20not%20suspect%20any%20foul%20play%20by%20anybody%20in%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20a%20c