ads%2F2024%2F03%2F07202747%2FTWW.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fourth%20episode%20of%20%E2%80%98The%20Wire%20Wrap%E2%80%99%2C%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%20is%20joined%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20founding%20editor%20M.K.%20Venu%20and%20senior%20journalist%20Javed%20Ansari.%20The%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20filed%20a%20contempt%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20(March%207)%20after%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20disobeyed%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20deadline%20of%20March%206%20to%20furnish%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20last%20month%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20while%20declaring%20electoral%20bonds%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D%20had%20directed%20SBI%20to%20furnish%20a%20list%20of%20names%20of%20those%20who%20had%20purchased%20electoral%20bonds%20for%20their%20favoured%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SBI%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20sought%20time%20till%20June%2030%2C%20which%20is%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20to%20furnish%20these%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20released%20its%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20which%20included%20195%20names%20and%20only%2028%20women.%20While%2034%20central%20ministers%20were%20retained%2C%20the%20list%20saw%20exclusions%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20among%20ministers%20and%20other%20controversial%20MPs%20like%20Sadhvi%20Pragya%20Thakur%2C%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20paper%20leaks%20and%20cancellations%20continue%20to%20jolt%20job%20aspirants%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20with%20the%20RO%20and%20ARO%20exams%20being%20cancelled%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%2050%20lakh%20aspirants%20being%20affected%20by%20paper%20leaks%20in%20the%20state%2C%20unemployment%20once%20again%20emerg