more%20open%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20keen%20to%20maximise%20its%20returns%20from%20the%20southern%20states%2C%20particularly%20since%20the%20general%20consensus%20is%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20again%20dominate%20heartland%20and%20Hindi-speaking%20states%3B%20in%202019%20the%20saffron%20party%20won%20185%20seats%20from%20this%20belt%2C%20while%20its%20main%20rival%20won%20a%20shockingly%20poor%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-holds-first-meet-to-pick-candidates-10-states-60-seats-on-table-5195009%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECongress'%201st%20Meet%20To%20Pick%20Candidates.%2010%20States%2C%2060%20Seats%20On%20Table%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20south%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20where%20the%20Congress%20will%20most%20likely%20make%20the%20most%20gains%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20an%20absolute%20increase%20in%20percentage%20of%20seats%20contested%20and%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%2C%20where%20it%20is%20now%20in%20power%20after%20outstanding%20performances%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20of%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarnataka%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20sends%2028%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20but%20in%202019%20the%20Congress%20won%20only%20one%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20change%20in%20its%20favour%20after%20the%20party's%20strong%20showing%20in%20last%20year's%20Assembly%20election%2C%20except%20that%20historically%20the%20state%20doesn't%20vote%20in%20a%20general%20election%20as%20it%20does%20in%20a%20state%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20though%2C%20is%20keen%20to%20put%20up%20a%20strong%20fight%20and%20has%20tapped%20senior%20members%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah's%20government%20as%20potent