ns%20related%20to%20drone%20warfare%20and%20how%20they%20can%20be%20countered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELt%20General%20Sunil%20Srivastava%20(retired)%2C%20Former%20Director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Joint%20Warfare%20Studies%2C%20suggested%20some%20ways%20to%20counter%20such%20threats.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20maiden%20NDTV%20Defence%20Summit%2C%20General%20Srivastava%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBoth%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20have%20built%20an%20ecosystem%20of%20drones%2C%20mass%20production%20is%20taking%20place.%20Crowdsourcing%20and%20volunteers%20are%20coming%20up%20and%20drones%20are%20being%20produced%20without%20trial%20evaluation%20using%20various%20technologies%20on%20which%20their%20counter-jamming%20systems%20are%20not%20effective.%20Therefore%20the%20attrition%20rate%20is%20very%20high%20but%20it%20is%20letting%20them%20stay%20in%20the%20fight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20nets%2C%20laser%20systems%20like%20Israel's%20Iron%20Beam%2C%20and%20electronic%20jammers%20are%20currently%20the%20most%20effective%20and%20cheap%20ways%20to%20counter%20drones.%20The%20Israeli%20Iron%20Beam%20has%20been%20effective%20and%20I%20think%20lasers%2C%20and%20jammers%20are%20needed%20to%20counter%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20spike%20in%20the%20way%20robotic%20platforms%20are%20being%20used.%20It%20is%20indicating%20a%20doctrinal%20shift%20and%20robots%20are%20here%20to%20play%20an%20important%20role%20and%2010-15%25%20of%20robots%20will%20be%20there%20in%20future%20forces.%20This%20indicates%20two%20things%20-%20Drone%20help%20in%20persistence%20in%20Tactical%20Battle%20Areas%20(TBA)%20and%20the%20combination%20of%20AI%2C%20and%20modern%20tech%20can%20make%20any%20cheap%20drone%20very%20powerful%2C%26quot%3B%20Sameer%20Joshi%2C%20a%20defence%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Ukrainian%20drones%20attacked%20a%20metal%20plant%20in%20Russia's%20border%20region%20of%20Kursk%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20causing%20a%20fire%20at%20a%20fuel%20tank%2C%20the%20local%20governor%20said.Kyiv%20meanwhile%20announced%20it%20had%20intercepted%20dozens%20of%20Russian%20drones%2C%20as%20both%20sides%20launched%20a%20wave%20of%20overnight%20aerial%20attacks%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20hit%20targets%20deep%20behind%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20forces%20have%20launched%20a%20wave%20of%20drone%20attacks%20at%20Russian%20energy%20facilities%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20trying%20to%20target%20the%20country's%20vital%20energy%20and%20gas%20sector%20that%20it%20says%20Russia%20uses%20to%20fuel%20its%20invasion.%20Ukraine%20also%20said%20that%20Russia%20fired%2042%20Iran-designed%20attack%20drones%20and%20five%20missiles%20at%20its%20territory%20overnight%20in%20a%20barrage%20that%20injured%20at%20least%20seven%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoitering%20munitions%20and%20robots%20are%20cheap%20and%20using%20conventional%20missiles%20proves%20costly%20according%20to%20a%20cost-benefit%20analysis.%20For%20example%3A%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%20system%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20air%20defense%20systems%20in%20the%20world%20with%20over%2090%25%20efficacy%20but%20a%20salvo%20of%20rockets%20fired%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207%20proved%20how%20the%20system%20can%20be%20overwhelmed.%20A%20Tamir%20Missile%20of%20the%20system%20costs%20around%20%24100%2C000%20and%20a%20Hamas%20rocket%20is%20worth%20%24500.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709822340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F3un9tu5g_ukraine-drone_625x300_10_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-defence-summit-how-drones-are-helping-ukraine-fight-war-against-russia-what-expert-lt-general-sunil-srivastava-sameer-joshi-said-5195217%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Drones%20offer%20a%20%26quot%3Brisk-free%26quot%3B%20solution%20on%20a%20battlefield.%20An%20unmanned%20vehicle%20that%20can%20conduct%20strikes%2C