0been%20working%20in%20the%20government%20since%202005%20but%20I%20get%20only%20Rs%202%2C000%20monthly%20salary.%20If%20the%20prime%20minister%20would%20look%20into%20our%20issue%2C%20it%20would%20be%20nice%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20woman%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Kupwara%E2%80%99s%20Chowkibal%20village%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20Ahmad%20said%20that%20he%20left%20his%20home%20in%20the%20Kangan%20town%20of%20central%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Ganderbal%20district%20at%205%20in%20the%20morning%20along%20with%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20youngsters.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20we%20reached%20the%20stadium%2C%20we%20were%20told%20it%20was%20already%20full.%20We%20had%20high%20hopes%20of%20getting%20an%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20high%20unemployment%20in%20Kashmir%20because%20of%20which%20our%20youngsters%20are%20ending%20their%20lives%20by%20suicide.%20We%20want%20him%20%5Bthe%20prime%20minister%5D%20to%20address%20this%20issue.%20The%20government%20should%20also%20waive%20off%20our%20electricity%20fees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20youngster%20accompanying%20Irfan%2C%20who%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20immediately%20identified%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20come%20with%20high%20hopes%20to%20meet%20the%20prime%20minister%20but%20we%20were%20shifted%20to%20another%20stadium%20and%20made%20to%20sit%20there.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20unemployment%20in%20Kashmir.%20Our%20sisters%20are%20getting%20divorced%20within%20days%20of%20marriage.%20The%20government%20should%20address%20the%20uncertainties%20of%20Kashmiri%20youngsters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMd%20Sohail%20Akhtar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Bihar%2C%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20stadium.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20about%20our%20problems.%20We%20work%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20and%20whenever%20there%20is%20some%20issue%20and%20businesses%20shut%20down%2C%20we%20are%20under%20pressure.%20It%20affects%20our%20earnings.%20Even%20today%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhulam%20Mohammad%20Parray%2C%2078%2C%20who%20had%20come%20from%20Beerwah%20in%20central%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Budgam%20district%20said%20that%20he%20took%20a%20bank%20loan%20for%20the%20marriage%20of%20his%20daughters.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20applied%20for%20some%20financial%20assistance%20in%20the%20social%20welfare%20department.%20I%20was%20hoping%20to%20meet%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Esaheb%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20seek%20his%20help%20but%20the%20security%20forces%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20me%20inside%20the%20venue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07193934%2Fimage-1918.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07193934%2Fimage-1918.png%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07193934%2Fimage-1918-300x188.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07193934%2Fimage-1918-1024x642.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700685%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22677%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20long%20queue%20of%20people%20standing%20outside%20the%20venue%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rally%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20on%20March%207.%20Photo%3A%20Ubaid%20Mukhtar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDynastic%20politics%20and%20corruption%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20stadium%2C%20Modi%20again%20targeted%20dynastic%20politics%2C%20without%20taking%20any%20names%2C%20and%20corruption%2C%20which%20he%20claimed%20were%20responsible%20for%20all%20the%20problems%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20%E2%80%9CDynastic%20politics%20and%20corruption%20were%20long-standing%20problems%20but%20we%20have%20taken%20care%20of%20these%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20a%20fervent%20poll%20pitch%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20central%20government%20has%20empowered%20the%20backward%20and%20disadvantaged%20sections%20of%20society%20by%20providing%20reservation%20benefits%20to%20the%20Schedule%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20new%20J%26amp%3BK%20for%20which%20we%20all%20have%20yearned%20for%20decades.%20This%20is%20a%20new%20J%26amp%3BK%20for%20which%20Syama%20Prasad%20Mukherjee%20sacrificed%20his%20life.%20In%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20new%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20there%20is%20a%20glitter%20of%20a%20(good)%20future.%20This%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20determination%20to%20defeat%20the%20challenges%20of%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20speech%2C%20Modi%20also%20announced%20the%20start%20of%20a%20campaign%20to%20promote%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20a%20wedding%20destination.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20starting%20%E2%80%98Wed%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20campaign.%20I%20urge%20those%20planning%20weddings%20to%20come%20and%20stay%20here%20for%20three%20to%20four%20days%20and%20spend%20lavishly%20so%20that%20locals%20can%20earn%20their%20bread%20and%20butter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20said%20that%20he%20has%20been%20asking%20tourists%20to%20visit%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20purchase%20local%20products.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20bought%20something%20from%20Srinagar%20today.%20I%20want%20to%20strengthen%20the%20economy%20which%20will%20open%20new%20avenues%20of%20employment%20for%20locals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cwon%E2%80%99t%20leave%20any%20stone%20unturned%20to%20repay%20the%20debt%20of%20the%20love%20given%20to%20me%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20working%20hard%20to%20win%20your%20hearts%20and%20I%20am%20seeing%20that%20I%20am%20on%20the%20right%20track.%20I%20have%20won%20your%20hearts%20and%20I%20will%20strive%20to%20win%20your%20hearts%20even%20more.%20This%20is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CModi%20%3Cem%3Esenz%3C%2Fem%3E%20guarantee%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%2C%20in%20Kashmiri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Modi%20was%20addressing%20the%20crowd%20in%20the%20stadium%2C%20a%20video%20clip%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%20showing%20a%20woman%2C%20who%20attended%20the%20rally%2C%20regretting%20that%20she%20and%20other%20employees%20were%20not%20provided%20water%20or%20refreshments%20by%20the%20government%20despite%20making%20it%20to%20the%20venue%20from%20far-flung%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20left%20home%20at%203%20am%20because%20of%20our%20prime%20minister%20Modiji.%20I%20work%20with%20the%20social%20welfare%20department%20but%20I%20have%20come%20here%20as%20an%20ordinary%20citizen.%20Unfortunately%2C%20our%20department%20didn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20us%20any%20refreshment.%20We%20have%20been%20hungry%20since%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20video%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20by%20Mehbooba%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20Iltija%20Mufti%2C%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Modi%20inaugurated%20and%20dedicated%20multiple%20developmental%20projects%20worth%20Rs%206%2C400%20crore%20and%20also%20distributed%20appointment%20letters%20to%20approximately%201%2C000%20new%20government%20recruits%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20Modi%20reportedly%20also%20launched%2043%20projects%20aimed%20at%20developing%20pilgrimage%20and%20tourist%20sites%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709819244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07190141%2Fimage-1915.png%2