rd.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fmoody-s-ups-gdp-forecast-india-to-remain-fastest-growing-g20-nation-124030700902_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20deboards%20Religare%20Enterprises%20Chairperson%20Saluja%20from%20UK%20flight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709818860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F03%2Ffull%2F1699004572-9777.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-deboards-religare-enterprises-chairperson-saluja-from-uk-flight-124030700965_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20incident%20happened%20on%20flight%20AI%20161%20before%20the%20scheduled%20pushback%20for%20take%20off%20and%20Saluja%20was%20deboarded%20following%20advice%20from%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20flight%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-deboards-religare-enterprises-chairperson-saluja-from-uk-flight-124030700965_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-deboards-religare-enterprises-chairperson-saluja-from-uk-flight-124030700965_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-deboards-religare-enterprises-chairperson-saluja-from-uk-flight-124030700965_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Slash%20in%20Budget%20for%20PM's%20Matru%20Vandana%20Yojana%2C%20Lack%20of%20Health%20Infrastructure%20Worry%20Pregnant%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F18171021%2Fpregnant-woman-under-cloudy-sky-in-silhouette-photography-1717292.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20spent%20around%20Rs%2010%2C000%20on%20my%20pregnancy%2C%20including%20travelling%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rubeena%20Sheikh%20said%2C%20with%20a%20quick%20glance%20at%20her%20mother-in-law%2C%20a%20movement%20she%20makes%20at%20the%20end%20of%20every%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFour%20days%20earlier%2C%20Rubeena%20had%20given%20birth%20to%20her%20second%20child%2C%20and%20she%20was%20waiting%20for%20the%20Rs%206%2C000%20allowance%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Matru%20Vandana%20Yojana%20(PMMVY)%2C%20a%20maternity%20support%20scheme%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20aimed%20at%20promoting%20healthy%20behaviour%20practices%20among%20pregnant%20women.%20Even%20though%20the%20scheme%20was%20introduced%20seven%20years%20ago%2C%20experts%20reveal%20turbulence%20in%20uptake%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjharkhandsfc.in%2Fpdf%2Fintrn_rprt%2Frprt_divya_chiraya.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eimplementation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20scheme%2C%20and%20raise%20concerns%20over%20its%20budgetary%20allocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FPMMVY%2520Scheme%2520Implemetation%2520Guidelines%2520._0.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Matru%20Vandana%20Yojana%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20initiated%20in%202017%20as%20per%20provisions%20under%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdfpd.gov.in%2FWriteReadData%2FOther%2Fnfsa_1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENational%20Food%20Safety%20Act%2C%202013%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20provides%20financial%20support%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20for%20pregnant%20women%20and%20lactating%20mothers%20during%20the%20first%20pregnancy%2C%20as%20compensation%20for%20partial%20wage%20loss%2C%20and%20to%20improve%20the%20wellbeing%20and%20health-seeking%20behaviour%20of%20the%20mother%20and%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20scheme%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FMission%2520Shakti%2520Guidelines%2520for%2520implementation%2520during%252015th%2520Finance%2520Commission%2520period%25202021-22%2520to%25202025-26_1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eupdated%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20added%20to%20an%20overarching%20women%20empowerment%20scheme%20called%20Mission%20Shakti%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development.%20The%20revised%20scheme%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20PMMVY%202.0%2C%20sought%20to%20discourage%20female%20foeticide%20and%20offered%20an%20allowance%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F1714%2FAU1123.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqals%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERs%206%2C000%20to%20a%20second%20child%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0if%20the%20infant%20is%20a%20girl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EAgency%20and%20awareness%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERubeena%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Rafeeq%20Nagar%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20was%20one%20among%20the%2040%2C000%20homes%20with%20joint%20families%20crammed%20into%20one-room%20houses.%20With%20the%20closest%20accessible%20hospital%20over%206%20km%20away%2C%20she%20spoke%20of%20the%20hardships%20of%20getting%20tests%20and%20paperwork%20done%20for%20availing%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FFAQ_PMMVY%25202.0-2.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETo%20apply%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20the%20scheme%2C%20women%20are%20required%20to%20produce%20their%20bank%20account%20details%2C%20government%20identification%20cards%20including%20Aadhaar%20and%20ration%20cards%20along%20with%20registration%20details%20of%20their%20mother%20and%20child%20protection%20card%20(MCP)%2C%20which%20records%20the%20date%20of%20pregnancy%20as%20the%20date%20of%20their%20last%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20women%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20their%20ration%20cards%20updated%20with%20their%20husband%E2%80%99s%20family%20details%20or%20have%20a%20registered%20bank%20account%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sabrin%20Sheikh%2C%20a%20staff%20member%20from%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnalaya.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EApnalaya%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20non-profit%20that%20works%20to%20increase%20awareness%20of%20government%20schemes%20in%20impoverished%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CGetting%20these%20done%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20as%20they%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20travel%20unless%20accompanied%20by%20their%20husband%20or%20mother-in-law.%20The%20husbands%20are%20mostly%20informal%20sector%20workers%20who%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20time%20to%20go%20after%20these%20things.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFor%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FFAQ_PMMVY%25202.0-2.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eeach%20instalment%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20come%20through%2C%20a%20set%20of%20conditions%20have%20to%20be%20met%2C%20including%20conducting%20antenatal%20checkups%20and%20registering%20the%20pregnancy%20and%20getting%20immunisation%20shots%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20last%20instalment.%20%E2%80%9CMostly%2C%20they%20deliver%20the%20baby%20by%20the%20time%20these%20records%20are%20obtained%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sheikh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07155304%2FPMMVY1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221034%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07155304%2FPMMVY1.png%201034w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07155304%2FPMMVY1-300x188.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07155304%2FPMMVY1-1024x643.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700625%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22649%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWomen%20in%20rural%20households%2C%20especially%20with%20low%20levels%20of%20education%2C%20experience%20a%20significant%20lack%20of%20agency.%20In%20rural%20India%2C%20only%2046%25%20of%20women%20own%20property%20alone%20or%20with%20others%2C%20while%2046%25%20have%20a%20mobile%20phone%20that%20they%20themselves%20used%2C%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.mohfw.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FNFHS-5_Phase-II_0.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENational%20Health%20Survey%2C%202019-21%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(NFHS-5).%20The%20expectation%20that%20girls%20should%20conform%20to%20social%20and%20family%20expectations%20and%20refrain%20from%20independent%20action%20structures%20their%20lives%20and%20thoughts%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasercentre.org%2Faser-2023-beyond-basics%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EASER%202023%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0report%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECultural%20traditions%20and%20beliefs%20also%20add%20to%20the%20means%20of%20restriction%20of%20women.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20choice%20does%20not%20lie%20with%20the%20mother.%20There%20is%20a%20stigma%20around%20revealing%20pregnancy%20in%20the%20first%20trimester%2C%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20attract%20the%20%E2%80%98evil%20eye%E2%80%99.%20If%20you%20really%20look%20at%20it%2C%20the%20problem%20boils%20down%20to%20lack%20of%20awareness%20and%20change%20of%20mindset%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rama%20Nath%2C%20Project%20Director%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.snehamumbai.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESociety%20for%20Nutrition%2C%20Education%20and%20Health%20Action%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOnly%2054%25%20of%20pregnant%20women%20from%20rural%20areas%20had%20at%20least%20four%20antenatal%20visits%20and%2067%25%20had%20an%20antenatal%20checkup%20in%20the%20first%20trimester%2C%20according%20to%20NFHS-5.%20Antenatal%20care%20can%20reduce%20health%20risks%20for%20mothers%20and%20babies%20as%20it%20includes%20monitoring%20pregnancies%20and%20screening%20for%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbmcpregnancychildbirth.biomedcentral.com%2Farticles%2F10.1186%2Fs12884-023-06002-9%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dand%2520unintended%2520pregnancy.-%2CPregnancy%2520registration%2520will%2520enhance%2520maternal%2520healthcare%2520utilization%2520and%2520reduce%2520adverse%2Cchildren%252C%2520thus%2520ensuring%2520better%2520health.%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EProactive%20registration%20of%20pregnancy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20general%20awareness%20about%20health%20and%20well-being%20during%20pregnancy%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%2C%20experts%20say.%20Women%20need%20to%20take%20the%20initiative%20and%20access%20the%20services%20available%20to%20them%2C%20but%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20coin%20is%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3484741%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DData%2520from%2520NFHS%252D3%2520reveal%2C(34%2525)%2520(12).%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Equality%20of%20the%20service%20offered%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3ECrippling%20lack%20of%20services%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAdequate%20maternal%20care%20and%20rest%20are%20essential%20for%20intrauterine%20growth%20and%20can%20affect%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20birth%20weight.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicef.org%2Frosa%2Fpress-releases%2F2018-global-nutrition-report-reveals-malnutrition-unacceptably-high-and-affects%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUNICEF%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0reported%20in%202018%20that%20India%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20malnourished%20children%20in%20the%20world%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%2046.6%20million%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20five%20suffering%20from%20stunting.%20Due%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7725295%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eeconomic%20and%20social%20difficulties%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20many%20women%20in%20impoverished%20India%20continue%20to%20toil%20away%20at%20work%20till%20they%20give%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAbout%201.3%20million%20maternal%20deaths%20occurred%20between%201997%20and%202020%2C%20with%20about%2023%2C800%20in%202020.%20Most%20maternal%20deaths%20occur%20in%20the%20poorer%20states%20(63%25)%20and%20among%20women%20aged%2020-29%20years%2C%20according%20to%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10239284%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estudy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0published%20in%20the%20National%20Library%20of%20Medicine.%20Most%20mothers%20end%20up%20going%20back%20to%20work%20sooner%20than%20they%20should%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20causes%20harmful%20consequences%20for%20both%20the%20mother%20and%20the%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9COur%20country%20is%20large%20but%20the%20infrastructure%20per%20capita%20is%20miniscule%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dileep%20Mavlankar%2C%20professor%20and%20director%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fphfi.org%2Fiiphs%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EIndian%20Institute%20of%20Public%20Health%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9COur%20public%20health%20system%20has%20not%20improved%20despite%20the%20pandemic.%20Normally%2C%20the%20nurse%20to%20patient%20ratio%20is%204%3A1%20but%20in%20our%20public%20health%20centres%2C%20we%20have%20even%20100%3A1.%20The%20public%20health%20centres%20in%20rural%20areas%20have%20only%20one%20auxiliary%20nurse%2C%20not%20even%20a%20fully%20qualified%20one.%20We%20need%20to%20improve%20emergency%20auxiliary%20care%20and%20appoint%20skilled%20midwives.%20We%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20health%20education%20so%20that%20people%20can%20become%20better%20educated%20about%20their%20own%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EChanges%20and%20delays%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EApart%20from%20the%20general%20lack%20of%20awareness%20about%20government%20schemes%2C%20people%20are%20discouraged%20from%20applying%20or%20accessing%20the%20schemes%20due%20to%20changes%20in%20guidelines%20and%20taking%20the%20effort%20to%20avail%20them%20by%20procuring%20all%20the%20required%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20are%20revisions%20in%20schemes%2C%20people%20who%20are%20unaware%20are%20turned%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rama%20Nath.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20very%20discouraging%20and%20makes%20people%20think%20the%20scheme%20or%20the%20portal%20is%20just%20not%20working.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20scheme%20offering%20maternal%20services%20has%20changed%20names%20and%20norms%20four%20times.%20It%20began%20as%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2Fnewsite%2FPrintRelease.aspx%3Frelid%3D101782%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EIndira%20Gandhi%20Matritva%20Sahyog%20Yojana%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20launched%20in%20October%202010%20to%20provide%20cash%20incentives%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%20in%20three%20instalments%20for%20improving%20health%20and%20nutrition%20status%20of%20pregnant%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20government%20under%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20office%2C%20the%20scheme%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-renames-maternity-benefit-scheme-adds-pradhan-mantri-to-it%2Fstory-3hEL3x7FVEiEh3Oy88EYCN.html%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erenamed%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Matritva%20Vandana%20Yojana%2C%20and%20then%20again%20to%20PMMVY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%20as%20we%20said%2C%20PMMVY%20was%20clubbed%20within%20an%20overarching%20women%20empowerment%20scheme%20called%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FMission%2520Shakti%2520Guidelines%2520for%2520implementation%2520during%252015th%2520Finance%2520Commission%2520period%25202021-22%2520to%25202025-26_1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMission%20Shakti%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20continuous%20change%20of%20names%20causes%20confusion%2C%20hinders%20trust%20building%20and%20brand%20building.%20We%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20providing%20the%20basics%20instead%20of%20all%20this%20show%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mavlankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07155554%2FPMMVY2-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22770%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07155554%2FPMMVY2-1.png%20770w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07155554%2FPMMVY2-1-300x278.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700627%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22714%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20was%20a%207%25%20increase%20in%20beneficiaries%20registered%20under%20PMMVY%20from%202020%20to%202021%2C%20but%20by%20November%202022%2C%20the%20number%20of%20beneficiaries%20fell%20by%2046%25%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20in%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20according%20to%20a%20budget%20brief%20by%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faccountabilityindia.in%2Fpublication%2Fpradhan-mantri-matru-vandana-yojana-janani-suraksha-yojana-budget-briefs-2023-accountability-initiative-centre-for-policy-research%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAccountability%20Initiative%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20decline%20could%20be%20because%20of%20the%20new%20guidelines%20that%20state%20that%20benefits%20can%20be%20availed%20only%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20Aadhar%20numbers%20of%20eligible%20citizens%2C%20the%20brief%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20only%20aspect%20that%20remains%20the%20same%20is%20the%20compensation%20for%20the%20first%20live%20birth.%20It%20does%20not%20account%20for%20inflation%20and%20has%20remained%20the%20same%20since%202017.%20Adjusted%20for%20inflation%2C%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20compensation%20should%20have%20increased%20by%20at%20least%20Rs%201%2C599%20to%20Rs%206%2C599%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faccountabilityindia.in%2Fpublication%2Fpradhan-mantri-matru-vandana-yojana-janani-suraksha-yojana-budget-briefs-2023-accountability-initiative-centre-for-policy-research%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20Initiative%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EStalling%20instalments%20and%20decreasing%20budgets%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMaternity%20benefits%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.dashboard.nic.in%2Fview_detail%2FeyJpdiI6Ik1SWk9yNm9OS2VKWVVDejF5QWNyVlE9PSIsInZhbHVlIjoiQTNyOUdPTzZcL3NqVVpBbmpHRE04Y0E9PSIsIm1hYyI6IjdhMmY5NWU3NjYyOGFkZTJiYTBmNzRkNjMyZTI2YzcxOGQzYjIzNDM3NWI4MWYzNTNlMWU5YTJjNDRlODc3OTgifQ%3D%3D%2F2%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERs%2014%2C427%20crore%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0have%20been%20disbursed%20to%20over%2032.1%20million%20beneficiaries%20as%20of%20February%2019%2C%202024%2C%20the%20PMMVY%20dashboard%20shows.%20It%20is%20unclear%20how%20many%20women%20received%20both%20instalments%20under%20the%20scheme.%20For%20instance%2C%20only%2029%25%20of%20eligible%20citizens%20who%20had%20been%20paid%20had%20received%20all%20their%20instalments%20until%20November%202022%2C%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faccountabilityindia.in%2Fpublication%2Fpradhan-mantri-matru-vandana-yojana-janani-suraksha-yojana-budget-briefs-2023-accountability-initiative-centre-for-policy-research%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAccountability%20Initiative%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20scheme%2C%20as%20we%20said%2C%20is%20intended%20to%20make%20up%20for%20partial%20wage%20loss%20for%20pregnant%20women.%20The%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faccountabilityindia.in%2Fpublication%2Fpradhan-mantri-matru-vandana-yojana-janani-suraksha-yojana-budget-briefs-2023-accountability-initiative-centre-for-policy-research%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eminimum%20wage%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0prescribed%20by%20the%20government%20for%20unskilled%20workers%20is%20Rs%2012%2C270%20per%20month.%20The%20compensation%20provided%20under%20the%20scheme%20thus%20does%20not%20meet%20the%20financial%20requirements%20of%20pregnant%20women%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20continue%20unhealthy%20working%20practices%20during%20the%20time%20of%20pregnancy.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20budget%20allocated%20for%20the%20scheme%20in%202023-24%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F1711%2FAU3924.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqals%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edecreased%20by%2017%25%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20Rs%202%2C067%20crore%20from%20the%20amount%20allocated%20in%202020-21.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20decrease%20in%20budget%20is%20in%20tune%20with%20the%20overall%20lack%20of%20emphasis%20on%20quality%20healthcare%20in%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20a%20gross%20under%20investment%20in%20public%20health%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mavlankar.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20population%20surplus%20country%20and%20our%20leaders%20need%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20medical%20and%20public%20health%20is%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20that%20infrastructure.%20We%20have%20a%20disproportionate%20emphasis%20on%20infrastructure.%20Modernity%20means%20even%20rural%20people%20having%20access%20to%20quality%20healthcare.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFrom%206%2C000%20beneficiaries%20referred%20to%20the%20PMMVY%20between%20January%20and%20December%202023%20in%20a%20few%20parts%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20only%201%2C500%20were%20taken%20up%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.snehamumbai.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESociety%20for%20Nutrition%2C%20Education%20and%20Health%20Action%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(SNEHA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20its%20analysis%20for%20Budget%202023-24%2C%20Accountability%20Initiative%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faccountabilityindia.in%2Fpublication%2Fpradhan-mantri-matru-vandana-yojana-janani-suraksha-yojana-budget-briefs-2023-accountability-initiative-centre-for-policy-research%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eestimated%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20there%20were%2019.8%20million%20pregnant%20women%20and%20lactating%20mothers%20in%202022%2C%20over%2016.1%20million%20more%20than%20the%20enrolled%20eligible%20citizens%20in%202022-23.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20estimated%20cost%20for%20the%20first%20live%20birth%20under%20the%20scheme%20alone%20was%20three-fold%20higher%20than%20the%20allocations%20for%202022-23%2C%20the%20analysis%20showed.%20The%20estimated%20cost%20of%20second%20live%20birth%20payment%20results%20in%20an%20additional%20cost%20of%20Rs%202.05%20crore.%20This%20suggests%20that%20the%20existing%20allocations%20did%20not%20even%20cover%20for%20the%20first%20live%20birth%20in%202021-22%2C%20the%20analysis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07155635%2FPMMVY3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22748%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07155635%2FPMMVY3.png%20748w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07155635%2FPMMVY3-300x127.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700628%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22317%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20demand%2C%20but%20we%20are%20still%20cutting%20down%20on%20supply.%20This%20decrease%20in%20allocation%20is%20concerning%2C%20considering%20we%20have%20a%20large%20marginalised%20population.%20The%20Public%20Health%20department%20has%20been%20supportive%2C%20especially%20in%20working%20with%20civil%20society%20organisations%20but%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20referral%20and%20uptake%20requires%20a%20scientific%20analysis%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rama%20Nath%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.snehamumbai.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESNEHA%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20latest%20update%20for%20the%20scheme%20was%20the%20launch%20of%20an%20online%20portal%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1972286%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPMMVYsoft%20MIS%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202023%20through%20which%20beneficiaries%20are%20paid%20via%20direct%20account%20transfers.%20This%20change%20is%20intended%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20departments%20to%20manage%20data%20about%20beneficiaries%2C%20but%20only%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.mohfw.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FNFHS-5_Phase-II_0.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E46.6%25%20of%20women%20in%20rural%20India%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0are%20connected%20to%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EExperts%20urge%20the%20need%20of%20adequate%20evaluation%20of%20the%20schemes%20that%20are%20currently%20in%20place.%20Mavlankar%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20recording%20maternal%20mortality%20appropriately%2C%20we%20are%20not%20appointing%20statisticians.%20Evaluation%20of%20maternal%20child%20health%20programmes%20is%20simply%20not%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fgovernance%2Fpms-matru-vandana-yojana-budget-stagnates-despite-rise-in-beneficiaries-898351%5C%22%3Estory%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20first%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2F%5C%22%3EIndiaSpend%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%2C%20a%20data-driven%2C%20public-interest%20journalism%20non-profit.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709818215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F18171021%2Fpregnant-woman-under-cloudy-sky-in-silhouette-photography-1717292.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fslash-in-budget-for-pms-matru-vandana-yojana-lack-of-health-infrastructure-worry-pregnant-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20rising%20beneficiaries%2C%20the%20budget%20for%20PMMVY%20decreased%20in%202023-24%C2%A0by%2017%25%C2%A0to%20Rs%202%2C067%20crore%20from%20the%20amount%20allocated%20in%202020-21.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fslash-in-budget-for-pms-matru-vandana-yojana-lack-of-health-infrastructure-worry-pregnant-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20hospital%20where%20treatment%20is%20by%20torchlight%20and%20'13%20babies%20died%20of%20malnutrition%20on%20one%20day'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709817840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-gaza-bunkall_6481781.jpg%3F20240307141927%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthe-gaza-hospital-where-treatment-is-by-torchlight-and-13-babies-died-of-malnutrition-on-one-day-13089190%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20hospital%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20it's%20been%20claimed%2013%20babies%20died%20of%20malnutrition%20in%20a%20single%20day%20last%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A327%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthe-gaza-hospital-where-treatment-is-by-torchlight-and-13-babies-died-of-malnutrition-on-one-day-13089190%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fthe-gaza-hospital-where-treatment-is-by-torchlight-and-13-babies-died-of-malnutrition-on-one-day-13089190%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fthe-gaza-hospital-where-treatment-is-by-torchlight-and-13-babies-died-of-malnutrition-on-one-day-13089190%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20is%20a%20Wolf%20in%20Wolf's%20Clothing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F06142846%2FNHRC.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDemocracy%2C%20the%20highest%20form%20of%20human%20rights%2C%20is%20at%20peril%20in%20India%20today.%20The%202023%20V-Dem%20Institute%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Gothenburg%20in%20Sweden%20report%20refers%20to%20India%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20worst%20autocratisers%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%9D%20and%20places%20India%20in%20the%20bottom%2040-50%25%20on%20its%20Liberal%20Democracy%20Index%20at%20rank%2097%2C%20below%20even%20Nigeria.%20India%20also%20ranks%20108%20on%20the%20Electoral%20Democracy%20Index.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20same%20institute%20classified%20India%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-autocratiser-v-dem-report-2023%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Celectoral%20autocracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20such%20a%20decaying%20democracy%2C%20there%20are%20several%20factors%20that%20indicate%20clear%20and%20present%20danger%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20parliament%20that%20are%20just%20around-the-corner.%20People%20have%20also%20opposed%20the%20use%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20and%20demanded%20a%C2%A0%20return%20to%20the%20paper%20ballot%20in%20particular.%20The%20INDIA%20block%20of%20opposition%20parties%20has%20also%20echoed%20this%20demand.%20At%20the%20core%20of%20these%20demands%20is%20the%20scathing%20criticism%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%2C%20indicating%20that%20many%20have%20lost%20trust%20in%20the%20election%20watchdog.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUN%20High%20Commission%20for%20Human%20Rights%20has%20recognised%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20public%20affairs%20as%20a%20fundamental%20imperative.%20According%20to%20the%20commission%20genuine%20and%20credible%20elections%20remain%20the%20most%20compelling%20and%20effective%20way%20for%20people%20to%20participate%20in%20governance%20and%20have%20their%20voices%20heard.%20Genuine%20and%20credible%20elections%20are%20nourished%20by%20a%20complex%20ecosystem%20made%20up%20of%20interlocking%20human%20rights%20protections%3A%20the%20impartial%20rule%20of%20law%3B%20and%20respect%20for%20fundamental%20freedoms%20and%20essential%20rights%2C%20such%20as%20education%2C%20which%20empower%20people%20to%20make%20free%20and%20informed%20choices.%20And%20this%20fundamental%20human%20right%20imperative%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20is%20under%20grave%20threat%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVolker%20Turk%2C%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%20in%20his%20opening%20remarks%20at%20the%2055th%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fstatements-and-speeches%2F2024%2F03%2Fturks-global-update-human-rights-council%5C%22%3Esaid%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20India%2C%20with%20an%20electorate%20of%20960%20million%20people%2C%20the%20coming%20election%20will%20be%20unique%20in%20scale.%20I%20admire%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20secular%20and%20democratic%20traditions%20and%20its%20great%20diversity.%20I%20am%2C%20however%2C%20concerned%20by%20increasing%20restrictions%20on%20the%20civic%20space%20%E2%80%93%20with%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20journalists%20and%20perceived%20critics%20targeted%20%E2%80%93%20as%20well%20as%20by%20hate%20speech%20and%20discrimination%20against%20minorities%2C%20especially%20Muslims.%20It%20is%20particularly%20important%20in%20a%20pre-electoral%20context%20to%20ensure%20an%20open%20space%20that%20respects%20the%20meaningful%20participation%20of%20everyone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20look%20at%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20the%20farmers.%20In%20brazen%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20liberties%20enshrined%20in%20the%20constitution%2C%20Indian%20riot%20police%20in%20North-India%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Fen%2Findia%2Farticle%2F2024%2F02%2F14%2Findian-police-attempt-to-block-capital-from-protesting-farmers_6523305_168.html%23%5C%22%3Eexcessive%20force%20on%20farmers%20trying%20to%20reach%20New%20Delh%3C%2Fa%3Ei%20to%20demand%20guaranteed%20crop%20prices.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20lines%20of%20hundreds%20of%20tractors%20have%20been%20stalled%20by%20fearsome%20barricades%20of%20concrete%20blocks%20and%20lines%20of%20razor%20wire.%20Police%20have%20also%20ringed%20the%20capital%20on%20three%20sides%2C%20blocking%20highways%20with%20metal%20spikes%2C%20blocks%20and%20steel%20barricades%2C%20while%20mobile%20internet%20services%20have%20been%20cut.%20In%20places%2C%20deep%20ditches%20have%20been%20dug%20to%20stop%20the%20tractors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20another%20front%2C%20academics%20from%20around%20the%20world%20have%20urged%20India%20to%20cancel%20a%20huge%20construction%20project%20on%20Great%20Nicobar%20Island%2C%20warning%20it%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Ca%20death%20sentence%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20Shompen%20hunter-gatherer%20tribals%20who%20live%20there.%20The%20%249%20billion%20port%20project%2C%20planned%20to%20transform%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20island%20of%208%2C000%20inhabitants%20into%20what%20has%20been%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9CHong%20Kong%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20includes%20the%20construction%20of%20an%20international%20shipping%20terminal%2C%20airport%2C%20power%20plant%2C%20military%20base%20and%20industrial%20park.%20It%20will%20also%20develop%20tourism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffor-an-already-ailing-nhrc-justice-mishras-appointment-spells-further-doom%5C%22%3E%20For%20An%20Already%20Diminished%20NHRC%2C%20Justice%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20Appointment%20Spells%20Further%20Doom%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20open%20letter%20to%20the%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%2039%20scholars%20from%2013%20countries%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fglobal-development%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F07%2Findia-port-airport-power-plant-military-project-great-nicobar-island-death-sentence-shompen-indigenous-people-warning%5C%22%3Ewarned%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eif%20the%20project%20goes%20ahead%2C%20even%20in%20a%20limited%20form%2C%20we%20believe%20it%20will%20be%20a%20death%20sentence%20for%20the%20Shompen%2C%20tantamount%20to%20the%20international%20crime%20of%20genocide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20many%20more%20instances%20of%20similar%20nature%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthoothukudi-anti-sterlite-protest-vedanta-autopsy-report%5C%22%3Ecold-blooded%20killing%20of%2012%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20Thoothukudi%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fcorporate%2Fstory%2Fsetback-for-vedanta-group-as-sc-turns-down-plea-to-reopen-sterlite-copper-plant-in-tn-419555-2024-02-29%5C%22%3Edemanding%20the%20closure%20of%20poison-spilling%20Sterlite%20Copper%20smelter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20None%20of%20these%20cases%20of%20%E2%80%98murder%20of%20human%20rights%E2%80%99%20and%20even%20%E2%80%98genocide%20of%20tribals%E2%80%99%20has%20touched%20the%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20of%20India%20(NHRC)%20that%20is%20due%20for%20its%20next%20review%20for%20accreditation%20by%20the%20Global%20Alliance%20of%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Institutions%20(GANHRI)%20in%20March%202024.%20This%20will%20be%20the%20NHRCI%E2%80%99%E2%80%99s%20sixth%20round%20of%20accreditation%20following%20past%20processes%20in%202006%2C%202011%2C%202016%2C%202017%20and%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20NHRC%20has%20failed%20to%20protect%20basic%20human%20rights%20of%20citizens.%20The%20office-bearers%20are%20handpicked%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20charter%20of%20human%20rights%20remains%20merely%20on%20paper.%20Although%20meant%20to%20protect%20the%20citizens%2C%20the%20rights%20body%20has%20instead%20resorted%20to%20covering%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20violations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKavita%20Srivastava%2C%20national%20secretary%20of%20People%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%20puts%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Famp%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-news%2Farticle%2Fnhrc-failed-to-protecthuman-rights-2325987%5C%22%3Ebluntly%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20is%20the%20main%20violator%20of%20human%20rights%2C%20as%20per%20their%20data%20regarding%20the%20complaints.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20effort%20by%20the%20NHRC%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20For%20instance%2C%20has%20the%20NHRCI%20made%20any%20statement%20on%20anybody%E2%80%99s%20arrest%2C%20whether%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20conspiracy%20case%20or%20say%20Bilkis%20Banos%20accused%20getting%20remission%3F%20Hate%20crimes%20against%20Muslims%20galore%2C%20dissenters%20are%20being%20attacked%20all%20the%20time%2C%20but%20the%20NHRC%20is%20silent%E2%80%A6%20The%20body%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20act%20as%20a%20mechanism%20to%20protect%20human%20rights%20has%20lost%20its%20soul%2C%20so%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20having%20it%2C%20if%20this%20be%20the%20case%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reasons%20for%20the%20miserable%20performance%20of%20NHRC%20are%20not%20far%20to%20seek.%20Of%20the%20six%20foundational%20principles%20(Paris%20Principles)%20the%20composition%20and%20functioning%20of%20NHRC%20seriously%20violates%20at%20least%20three%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E(1)%20Independence%3A%20International%20law%20recognises%20that%20even%20though%20NHRI%E2%80%99s%20are%20State%20institutions%2C%20set%20up%20and%20funded%20by%20the%20State%2C%20NHRI%E2%80%99s%20must%20be%20independent%20from%20government%20and%20from%20NGOs.%20As%20one%20international%20document%20points%20out%2C%20NHRI%E2%80%99s%20must%20have%20legal%20independence%2C%20operational%20independence%2C%20policy%20independence%20and%20financial%20independence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E(2)%20Pluralism%3A%20ensuring%20that%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20NHRI%E2%80%99s%20reflects%20the%20social%20forces%20(from%20civilian%20society)%20who%20are%20the%20targets%20of%20social%20discrimination%2C%20inequality%20and%20rights%20violations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E(3)%20Accountability%3A%20The%20NHRC%E2%80%99s%20are%20morally%20accountable%20to%20the%20larger%20citizenry%20who%20is%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20brazen%20rights%20violations%20committed%20with%20impunity%20by%20state%20forces%20confident%20that%20they%20are%20always%20immune%20from%20being%20held%20accountable%20for%20their%20actions.%20While%20the%20NHRCs%20may%20comply%20with%20the%20legal%20accountability%20of%20placing%20reports%20before%20Parliament%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20owning%20up%20to%20their%20moral%20and%20ethical%20accountability%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20the%20current%20chairman%20of%20NHRC%2C%20Justice%20Arun%20Mishra%2C%20in%20June%202021%2C%20by%20tweaking%20the%20rules%20is%20a%20typical%20case%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffor-an-already-ailing-nhrc-justice-mishras-appointment-spells-further-doom%5C%22%3Edeliberate%20and%20brazen%20violation%20of%20basic%20principles%20of%20human%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20condemned%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3DJustice%2Bmishra%2BNHRC%2Bdeliberate%2Bblow%2Bto%2Bthe%2Bconstitution%26oq%3DJustice%2Bmishra%2BNHRC%2Bdeliberate%2Bblow%2Bto%2Bthe%2Bconstitution%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIICAEQABgWGB4yDQgCEAAYhgMYgAQYigXSAQgzNzQwajBqNKgCALACAA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cdeliberate%20blow%20to%20the%20constitution%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20activists%20and%20members%20of%20various%20human%20rights%20organisations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20analysis%20of%20his%20performance%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20revealed%20that%20in%20personal%20liberty%20matters%2C%20he%20tended%20to%20prefer%20a%20hard%20line%2C%20favouring%20state%20action%20over%20charges%20of%20violation%20of%20individual%20liberties.%20In%20land%20acquisition%20matters%2C%20his%20orders%20indicated%20a%20tendency%20to%20favour%20the%20state%20as%20against%20individual%20landowners%20who%20challenged%20the%20land%20acquisition.%20In%20short%2C%20in%20all%20politically%20sensitive%20cases%2C%20he%20always%20sided%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20or%20acted%20in%20a%20manner%20to%20help%20some%20of%20its%20top%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cases%20where%20Justice%20Mishra%20has%20appeared%20to%20have%20helped%20the%20Union%20government%C2%A0include%20the%20judge%20Loya%20case%2C%20Sahara-Birla%20corruption%20case%2C%20Sanjiv%20Bhat%20case%2C%20Haren%20Pandya%20case%20and%20bail%20for%20activists%20Anand%20Teltumbde%20and%20Gautam%20Navlakha%20%E2%80%93%20all%20cases%20of%20serious%20human%20rights%20violation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnational-human-rights-commision-chief-justice-arun-mushra-activists-condemn-appointment%5D%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20activists%20and%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20Justice%20Mishra%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20rewarded%20for%20having%20declared%20his%20fealty%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%20an%20international%20conference%2C%20calling%20him%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinternationally%20acclaimed%20visionary%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Cversatile%20genius%2C%20who%20thinks%20globally%20and%20acts%20locally%2C%E2%80%9D%20when%20he%20was%20still%20a%20sitting%20Supreme%20Court%20judge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20can%20a%20person%20who%20made%20an%20improper%20and%20unwarranted%20statement%20praising%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20his%20very%20presence%2C%20be%20trusted%20by%20people%20to%20act%20without%20fear%20or%20favour%20to%20protect%20their%20human%20rights%20violated%20by%20the%20government%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20statement%20read.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20NHRC%2C%20under%20Justice%20Mishra%2C%20state%20hegemony%20and%20%E2%80%98national%20security%E2%80%99%20far%20outweigh%20liberty%20and%20human%20rights%20of%20individuals.%20In%20this%20he%20is%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fajit-doval-was-my-batchmate-but-his-understanding-of-constitution-civil-society-is-flawed%2F771459%2F%5C%22%3Edictum%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20game%20of%20power%2C%20the%20ultimate%20justice%20lies%20with%20the%20one%20who%20is%20strong%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20his%20doctrine%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20new%20frontiers%20of%20war%2C%20what%20you%20call%20the%20fourth-generation%20warfare%2C%20is%20the%20civil%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20This%20means%20that%20the%20civil%20society%2C%20including%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98enemy%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99%20and%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20such.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20evident%20that%20the%20NHRC%20is%20%E2%80%98a%20wolf%20in%20wolf%E2%80%99s%20clothing%E2%80%99%20and%20should%20be%20dealt%20with%20as%20such.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%20is%20former%20Army%20and%20IAS%20Officer.%20He%20is%20the%20Coordinator%20of%20the%20Citizens%20Commission%20on%20Elections%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3EElectoral%20Democracy%E2%80%94An%20Inquiry%20into%20the%20Fairness%20and%20Integrity%20of%20Elections%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-id%3D%5C%22tooltip%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709816355000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F06142846%2FNHRC.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-national-human-rights-commission-is-a-wolf-in-wolfs-clothing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NHRC%20office-bearers%20are%20handpicked%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20charter%20of%20human%20rights%20remains%20merely%20on%20paper.%20Although%20meant%20to%20protect%20the%20citizens%2C%20the%20rights%20body%20has%20instead%20resorted%20to%20covering%20the%20government's%20violations.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-national-human-rights-commission-is-a-wolf-in-wolfs-clothing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98It%20Is%20Only%20by%20Chance%20That%20I%20Came%20Out%20of%20Prison%20Alive%E2%80%99%3A%20G.N.%20Saibaba%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07181050%2Fimage-1914.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20only%20by%20chance%20that%20I%20came%20out%20of%20prison%20alive%2C%E2%80%9D%2056-year-old%20former%20Delhi%20University%20professor%20S.N.%20Saibaba%20said%20in%20his%20first%20press%20briefing%20since%20his%20release%20from%20Nagpur%20Central%20jail%20on%20Thursday%20(March%207).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nagpur%20bench%20of%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20on%20March%205%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbombay-hc-acquits-g-n-saibaba-and-five-others-in-uapa-case%5C%22%3Eacquitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20and%20five%20others%20on%20%E2%80%9Cterrorism%E2%80%9D%20charges.%20Saibaba%2C%20who%20is%20wheelchair-bound%20and%20is%20over%2090%25%20handicapped%2C%20said%20he%20can%E2%80%99t%20move%20an%20inch%20without%20others%E2%80%99%20help.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20the%20toilet%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20bath%20without%20support%2C%20and%20I%20lived%20in%20jail%20without%20any%20relief%20for%20so%20long.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20day%20in%202017%2C%20a%20local%20court%20in%20Gadchiroli%20had%20convicted%20him%20and%20four%20others%20%E2%80%93%20Prashant%20Rahi%2C%20Mahesh%20Tikri%2C%20Hem%20Keshwdatta%20Mishra%2C%20and%20Pandu%20Narote%20%E2%80%93%20to%20life%20sentences.%20The%20sixth%20accused%2C%20Vijay%20Nan%20Tikri%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%2010%20years%20of%20rigorous%20punishment.%20Narote%2C%20who%20fell%20seriously%20sick%20while%20in%20jail%2C%20died%20in%20August%202022.%20Narote%20was%20only%2033%20years%20old%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaibaba%20suffered%20greatly%20while%20in%20jail.%20His%20wife%2C%20Vasantha%20Kumari%2C%20and%20his%20lawyers%20had%2C%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20complained%20of%20ill-treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20him%20while%20in%20custody.%20Vasantha%20had%20even%20made%20several%20desperate%20appeals%20both%20to%20the%20court%20and%20the%20state%20government%20seeking%20his%20release.%20She%20feared%20he%20would%20die%20if%20not%20released%20immediately.%20Saibaba%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20media%20on%20Thursday%2C%20said%20his%20condition%20has%20further%20deteriorated%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20in%20two%20years%20that%20the%20high%20court%20has%20acquitted%20him%20and%20others%20of%20all%20charges.%20On%20October%2014%2C%202022%2C%20a%20division%20bench%2C%20comprising%20Justice%20Rohit%20B.%20Deo%20and%20Anil%20Pansare%2C%20overturned%20the%20Gadchiroli%20session%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgment.%20The%20state%20immediately%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20was%20overturned.%20Justice%20Deo%20resigned%20soon%20after.%20The%20case%20was%20freshly%20heard%20on%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20direction%2C%20and%20once%20again%2C%20the%20very%20same%20court%2C%20comprising%20Justice%20Vinay%20G.%20Joshi%20and%20Justice%20Valimiki%20S.%20Menezes%2C%20acquitted%20Saibaba%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20in%20the%20lower%20court%20was%20handled%20by%20Nagpur-based%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20Surendra%20Gadling.%20Soon%20after%20the%20trial%20was%20completed%20in%20the%20Gadchiroli%20sessions%20court%2C%20Gadling%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case.%20Saibaba%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20said%20that%20his%20lawyer%20Gadling%20was%20targeted%20only%20for%20handling%20his%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lawyer%20who%20has%20all%20along%20fought%20for%20justice%2C%20who%20has%20represented%20hundreds%20and%20thousands%20of%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20from%20the%20region%20in%20court%2C%20and%20such%20a%20man%20is%20in%20jail.%20If%20justice%20has%20to%20be%20fully%20achieved%20in%20my%20case%2C%20then%20Gadling%20should%20be%20released%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaibaba%20also%20thanked%20his%20team%20of%20lawyers%20who%20defended%20him%20in%20the%20high%20court.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20once%20but%20twice%20they%20(the%20lawyers)%20had%20to%20defend%20me%20in%20the%20high%20court.%20It%20has%20not%20been%20easy%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Saibaba%20was%20released%20only%20a%20few%20hours%20before%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20have%20the%20chance%20to%20read%20the%20judgment%20in%20his%20case.%20When%20asked%20if%20he%20would%20legally%20demand%20compensation%20from%20the%20state%2C%20Saibaba%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20health%20condition%20is%20not%20good.%20I%20have%20not%20thought%20about%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaibaba%20also%20spoke%20about%20Narote%20who%20died%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20adequate%20medical%20care%20in%20prison.%20%E2%80%9CA%20young%20man%2C%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20most%20primitive%20tribe%2C%20had%20to%20languish%20in%20jail%20with%20us.%20He%20had%20a%20young%20daughter.%20He%20suffered%20so%20much.%20Is%20justice%20really%20done%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%20Narote%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20Swine%20Flu%20and%20his%20lawyers%20and%20family%20members%20had%20accused%20the%20prison%20authorities%20for%20not%20attending%20to%20him%20on%20time%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20high%20court%20passed%20the%20judgment%20on%20March%205%2C%20Saibaba%20was%20released%20from%20prison%20only%20today.%20His%20lawyer%20Nihalsing%20Rathod%20attributed%20the%20delay%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20handedness%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Nagpur%20Central%20prison%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20first%20finish%20paperwork%20at%20the%20Gadchiroli%20court%20and%20then%20submit%20the%20release%20papers%20to%20the%20jail%20authorities.%20When%20we%20submitted%20it%20around%206%3A15%20pm%20on%20March%206%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20the%20release%20time%20was%20over%20for%20the%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rathod%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Other%20prisoners%2C%20not%20related%20to%20this%20case%2C%20however%2C%20were%20released%20from%20jail%20even%20as%20late%20as%208%20pm.%20Rathod%20had%20to%20submit%20a%20written%20complaint%20to%20the%20superintendent%20of%20Nagpur%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%207%2C%20however%2C%20the%20release%20formalities%20were%20completed%2C%20and%20Saibaba%20and%20Rahi%20were%20released%20in%20the%20morning.%20Mishra%2C%20who%20was%20lodged%20at%20the%20Kolhapur%20prison%2C%20was%20released%20by%20afternoon.%20Formalities%20for%20Vijay%20and%20Mahesh%E2%80%99s%20release%20continued%20until%20late%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMishra%E2%80%99s%20parents%2C%20who%20traveled%20from%20their%20hometown%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20had%20made%20a%20pit%20stop%20in%20Mumbai%20before%20heading%20to%20Kolhapur.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20found%20out%20that%20their%20lawyer%20Gadling%20would%20be%20produced%20before%20the%20NIA%20court%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20short%20detour%20to%20meet%20him%20and%20thank%20him.%20After%20the%20brief%20visit%2C%20they%20headed%20to%20Kolhapur%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20persons%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709815621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07181050%2Fimage-1914.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fit-is-only-by-chance-that-i-came-out-of-prison-alive-g-n-saibaba%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'I%20can%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20the%20toilet%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20bath%20without%20support%2C%20and%20I%20lived%20in%20jail%20without%20any%20relief%20for%20so%20long%2C'%20the%20former%20Delhi%20University%20professor%20said%20in%20his%20first%20press%20briefing%20since%20his%20release%20from%20Nagpur%20Central%20jail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C