blic-debt-issue-124030700847_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20came%20days%20after%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20barred%20JM%20Financial%20Products%20Ltd%20from%20providing%20any%20form%20of%20financing%20against%20shares%20and%20debentures%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsebi-bars-jm-financial-from-acting-as-lead-manager-of-any-public-debt-issue-124030700847_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsebi-bars-jm-financial-from-acting-as-lead-manager-of-any-public-debt-issue-124030700847_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsebi-bars-jm-financial-from-acting-as-lead-manager-of-any-public-debt-issue-124030700847_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Take%20Five%3A%20Congress%20Seizes%20Its%20%E2%80%98Guarantee%E2%80%99%20Mantra%2C%20Promises%20Govt%20Jobs%2C%20Safety%20Net%20for%20Gig%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F26210652%2FFufcgtmX0AQCmkG.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20on%20Thursday%20(March%207)%20promised%20a%20%E2%80%9Crozgaar%20revolution%E2%80%9D%20if%20it%20is%20voted%20to%20power%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%20five%20guarantees%20to%20bring%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eyuva%20nyay%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(justice%20to%20the%20youth)%20through%20employment%20including%20assurances%20of%20a%20right%20to%20apprenticeship%2C%20end%20to%20paper%20leaks%2C%20social%20security%20for%20the%20gig%20economy%2C%20filling%20vacant%20posts%20for%20government%20jobs%20and%20a%20startup%20fund.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Banswara%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20former%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20unemployment%20is%20the%20biggest%20issue%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnemployment%20is%20the%20biggest%20issue%20in%20the%20country.%20So%20today%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20what%20the%20Congress%20is%20doing%20for%20the%20yuva%20of%20the%20country%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20adivasi%20and%20Dalits%20of%20this%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20have%20counted%20that%20there%20are%2030%20lakh%20government%20vacancies%20in%20the%20country.%20Modi%20ji%20is%20not%20filling%20these%20vacancies.%20Our%20first%20goal%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20is%20that%2030%20lakh%20government%20jobs%20will%20be%20given.%20Second%2C%20we%20brought%20MGNREGA%20(Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act)%20that%20gave%20employment%20guarantees%20to%20lakhs.%20Similarly%20we%20will%20give%20the%20right%20to%20apprenticeship%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20this%20country.%20This%20apprenticeship%20will%20be%20given%20to%20all%20graduates%20and%20diploma%20holders.%20For%20one%20year%20every%20graduate%20in%20private%2C%20public%20offices%20will%20be%20given%20apprenticeship%20along%20with%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20This%20will%20be%20a%20MGNREGA-like%20right.%20This%20will%20benefit%20crores%20of%20youth%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20during%20his%20previous%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20country%20had%20spoken%20to%20him%20about%20paper%20leaks%20and%20exams%20to%20government%20posts%20being%20cancelled%20due%20to%20such%20leaks.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Futtar-pradesh-exams-cancellations-protests%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20in%20the%20last%20month%20over%2050%20lakh%20youth%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20paper%20leaks%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20alone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20bring%20a%20new%20legislation%20against%20paper%20leaks%20under%20which%20we%20will%20standardise%20the%20way%20in%20which%20exams%20are%20conducted%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20no%20outsourcing%20to%20private%20companies%20and%20only%20the%20government%20will%20hold%20exams.%20If%20paper%20leaks%20happen%20we%20will%20take%20such%20action%20that%20it%20is%20not%20repeated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20interim%20budget%20session%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20brought%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flok-sabha-passes-public-examinations-bill%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elegislation%20against%20paper%20leaks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20seeks%20to%20prevent%20paper%20leaks%20and%20malpractices%20in%20government%20recruitment%20examinations%20and%20provides%20for%20punishment%2C%20including%20imprisonment%20of%20up%20to%20ten%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20fourth%20guarantee%20is%20that%20it%20will%20bring%20a%20legislation%20for%20gig%20workers%20as%20it%20had%20brought%20in%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFourth%2C%20the%20youth%20of%20this%20country%20are%20engaged%20as%20gig%20workers%20in%20Ola%2C%20Uber%2C%20as%20well%20as%20delivery%20personnel.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20we%20brought%20a%20law%20to%20protect%20them%20with%20social%20security%20and%20pension.%20This%20law%20we%20will%20bring%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20fifth%20guarantee%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20start%20a%20Startup%20fund%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20called%20the%20Yuva%20Roshni%20Fund%20which%20will%20be%20at%20the%20district%20level%20to%20help%20youth%20to%20start%20their%20own%20businesses.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CModi%20started%20Startup%20India%2C%20Standup%20India%20and%20Make%20in%20India%20but%20that%20made%20no%20difference.%20It%20only%20benefitted%20big%20businesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20five%20guarantees%20for%20the%20youth%2C%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%20will%20also%20bring%20in%20a%20law%20guaranteeing%20MSP%20for%20farmers%2C%20and%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census%20which%20it%20had%20promised%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKharge%20said%20that%20while%20the%20BJP%20accuses%20the%20Congress%20of%20dynastic%20politics%2C%20whenever%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20been%20in%20power%20it%20has%20taken%20care%20of%20the%20poor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPandit%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20ji%20formed%20this%20country%20and%20the%20Constitution%20was%20brought%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar.%20The%20rights%20that%20we%20have%20is%20because%20of%20the%20blessings%20of%20Nehru%20and%20Ambedkar.%20They%20(BJP)%20only%20talk%20about%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eparivarvaad%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(dynasty%20politics).%20How%20many%20times%20will%20they%20repeat%20the%20same%20thing%3F%20Tell%20the%20people%20what%20work%20we%20have%20done.%20We%20can%20tell%20them%20about%20what%20we%20have%20done%3B%20what%20Indira%20Gandhi%20has%20done%3B%20what%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20ji%20has%20done%20or%20what%20Nehru%20ji%20has%20done.%20But%20what%20work%20have%20they%20done%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20five%20guarantees%20to%20the%20youth%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20committee%20which%20includes%20former%20finance%20minister%20P.%20Chidambaram%2C%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20presented%20the%20draft%20manifesto%20to%20Kharge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709814773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F26210652%2FFufcgtmX0AQCmkG.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frozgaar-revolution-congress-promises-rs-5000-cr-startup-fund-govt-jobs-safety-net-for-gig-work%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Calling%20unemployment%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbiggest%20issue%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%9D%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20unveiled%20the%20grand%20old%20party%E2%80%99s%20five%20assurances%20to%20bring%20yuva%20nyay%20(youth%20justice)%20if%20voted%20to%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frozgaar-revolution-congress-promises-rs-5000-cr-startup-fund-govt-jobs-safety-net-for-gig-work%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20to%20appeal%20ruling%20over%20Northern%20Ireland%20amnesty%20law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709814398000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108302571%2Cimgsize-20440.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fuk-to-appeal-ruling-over-northern-ireland-amnesty-law%2Farticleshow%2F108302482.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108302482.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20United%20Kingdom%20has%20appealed%20a%20Belfast%20court%20ruling%20that%20the%20law%20granting%20immunity%20to%20combatants%20involved%20in%20historic%20sectarian%20violence%20violated%20the%20European%20Convention%20on%20Human%20Rights.%20The%20Belfast%20High%20Court%20ruled%20that%20the%20law%20breached%20Ar