20would%20give%20me%20some%20more%20time.%20I%20will%20fight%20till%20I%20am%20alive.%20All%20I%20want%20to%20plead%20to%20CM%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20is%20to%20please%20give%20us%20%5Bjustice%5D%20in%20my%20lifetime.%20We%20want%20closure%20in%20this%20case.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07135631%2FIMG_4117.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07135631%2FIMG_4117.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07135631%2FIMG_4117-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700601%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBaldev%20Singh%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Baldip%20Kaur%2C%20at%20their%20home%20in%20Littran%20village%20in%20Nakodar.%20Photo%3A%20Kusum%20Arora.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20missing%20Justice%20Gurnam%20Singh%20report%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20extrajudicial%20killings%20of%20the%20four%20youth%20in%20February%201986%2C%20the%20then-finance%20minister%20Balwant%20Singh%20had%20announced%20a%20judicial%20inquiry%20by%20a%20retired%20high%20court%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20Justice%20Gurnam%20Singh%20Commission%20conducted%20the%20inquiry%20and%20submitted%20the%20%E2%80%98judicial%20inquiry%20report%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20Punjab%20government%20on%20October%2031%2C%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20first%20part%20of%20the%20inquiry%20report%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20Punjab%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20on%20March%205%2C%202001%2C%20when%20Parkash%20Singh%20Badal%20was%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20second%20part%20of%20the%20report%2C%20which%20was%20dated%20October%2031%2C%201986%20and%20contained%20significant%20evidence%2C%20exhibit%20files%20and%20the%20sworn%20statements%20of%20police%20officials%2C%20administrative%20authorities%20and%20witnesses%2C%20went%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20gap%20of%2033%20years%20and%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20families%2C%20the%20Punjab%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20speaker%20in%20a%20disclosure%20on%20February%2013%2C%202019%20revealed%20that%20the%20judicial%20inquiry%20report%20had%20been%20placed%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20on%20March%205%2C%202001%20without%20any%20action%20taken%20report%20and%20was%20accessible%20at%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20library%20before%20its%20second%20part%20disappearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Baldev%20Singh%20filed%20a%20petition%20regarding%20the%20missing%20second%20part%20of%20the%20report%20on%20August%2026%2C%202021%2C%20seeking%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20special%20investigative%20team%20(SIT)%20to%20investigate%20its%20disappearance%20from%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20Punjab%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20on%20my%20request%20to%20Punjab%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20speaker%20Kultar%20Singh%20Sandhawan%20that%20the%20SSP%20%5Bsenior%20superintendent%20of%20police%5D%20Jalandhar%20constituted%20%5Ban%20SIT%5D%C2%A0%20comprising%20SP%20%5Bsuperintendent%20of%20police%5D%20Jalandhar%2C%20DSP%20%5Bdeputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%5D%20Nakodar%20and%20SHO%20%5Bstation%20house%20officer%5D%20Nakodar%20was%20constituted%20on%20May%2012%2C%202023%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSSP%20Jalandhar%20Mukhwinder%20Singh%20Bhullar%20had%20directed%20the%20SIT%20to%20include%20me%20in%20the%20investigation%20and%20file%20a%20detailed%20report%20based%20on%20the%20findings%20and%20facts%20within%20one%20month.%20But%20six%20months%20have%20passed%20and%20nothing%20has%20been%20done%20in%20the%20name%20of%20investigating%20the%20extrajudicial%20killings%20of%20our%20sons%E2%80%9D%2C%20Baldev%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20months%20after%20the%20SIT%20was%20constituted%2C%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20Justice%20Avneesh%20Jhingan%20of%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20dismissed%20Baldev%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20petition%20and%20observed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLearned%20State%20Counsel%2C%20on%20instructions%20from%20Sukhpal%20Singh%2C%20DSP%20Sub%20Division%20Nakodar%2C%20District%20Jalandhar%20(Rural)%2C%20Inspector%20Satpal%20Singh%20Sidhu%2C%20SHO%20Police%20Station%20City%20Nakodar%20submitted%20that%20part%20of%20the%20inquiry%20report%20was%20misplaced.%20He%20further%20asserted%20that%20in%20response%20to%20the%20petitioner%E2%80%99s%20representation%2C%20an%20SIT%20was%20constituted.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20stated%20that%20four%20FIRs%20relating%20to%20the%20incident%20were%20registered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20distraught%20Baldev%20Singh%20also%20filed%20a%20right%20to%20information%20application%20on%20December%202%2C%202023%20but%20did%20not%20get%20any%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202024%2C%20Baldev%20Singh%20shot%20off%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Jalandhar%20SSP%20and%20urged%20him%20for%20action%20and%20transparency%20in%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20Nakodar%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20crucial%20witness%20of%20this%20case%20and%20the%20SIT%20was%20formed%20following%20my%20complaint.%20I%20want%20clarity%20as%20to%20how%20the%20report%20could%20be%20concluded%20without%20taking%20my%20account%20into%20consideration%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFamily%20holds%20first%20ever%20%3Cem%3Einsaf%20yatra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20demands%20discussion%20on%20Saka%20Nakodar%20in%20upcoming%20budget%20session%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaldev%20Singh%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Khalra%20Mission%20Organisation%2C%20Sikh%20Sadbhavna%20Dal%20and%20Alliance%20of%20Sikh%20Organisations%20on%20February%2028%2C%202024%20organised%20the%20first%20ever%20%E2%80%98insaf%20yatra%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98justice%20march%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20the%20Saka%20Nakodar%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07135747%2F3ea55f84-b24b-423e-aff9-f6379aee0f9f-1024x721.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07135747%2F3ea55f84-b24b-423e-aff9-f6379aee0f9f-1024x721.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07135747%2F3ea55f84-b24b-423e-aff9-f6379aee0f9f-300x211.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07135747%2F3ea55f84-b24b-423e-aff9-f6379aee0f9f.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700602%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22591%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBaldev%20Singh%20along%20with%20Sikh%20organisations%20during%20the%20insaf%20yatra%20on%20February%2028.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaswant%20Khalra%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Bibi%20Paramjit%20Kaur%2C%20who%20is%20a%20voice%20against%20extrajudicial%20killings%2C%20had%20been%20supporting%20the%20victims%20of%20Saka%20Nakodar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20justice%20march%2C%20they%20also%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Mann%20reminding%20him%20of%20his%20promise%20to%20provide%20them%20justice%20and%20sought%20a%20discussion%20on%20this%20case%20in%20the%20Punjab%20government%E2%80%99s%20budget%20session%20beginning%20from%20March%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20organise%20the%20insaf%20yatra%20on%20the%20same%20route%20from%20the%20Gurdwara%20Sahib%20in%20Sherpur%20to%20the%20Gurdwara%20Sri%20Guru%20Arjan%20Dev%20in%20Mohalla%20Nanakpura%2C%20Nakodar%20%E2%80%A6%20where%20the%20four%20youths%20had%20carried%20a%20peaceful%20march%20on%20February%204%2C%201986%E2%80%9D%2C%20Baldev%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20when%20Baldev%20Singh%20and%20the%20Sikh%20organisations%20were%20carrying%20out%20the%20insaf%20yatra%2C%20Mann%20was%20also%20in%20Nakodar%20for%20a%20state%20government%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20learnt%20that%20the%20Jalandhar%20rural%20police%20asked%20Baldev%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20family%20to%20stop%20the%20yatra%20as%20Mann%20was%20in%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarinder%20Singh%2C%20the%20US-based%20son%20of%20Baldev%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20SSP%20Jalandhar%20office%20sent%20us%20a%20message%20that%20we%20should%20postpone%20the%20insaf%20yatra.%20However%2C%20when%20we%20informed%20them%20that%20it%20was%20not%20possible%2C%20they%20asked%20us%20to%20change%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20yatra.%20It%20was%20only%20when%20we%20told%20the%20police%20that%20our%20yatra%20would%20be%20held%20from%2010%20am%20to%2011%3A30%20am%20that%20they%20allowed%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment%20withholds%20Saka%20Nakodar%20X%20page%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Saka%20Nakodar%201986%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20page%2C%20run%20by%20Harinder%20Singh%20from%20the%20US%2C%20was%20withheld%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Harinder%20Singh%20said%20that%20it%20was%20either%20a%20fallout%20of%20the%20ongoing%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20under%20which%20many%20social%20media%20accounts%20were%20being%20withheld%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20or%20the%20recent%20presentation%20of%20their%20case%20at%20the%20Congressional%20briefing%20on%20transnational%20repression%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20on%20February%2014%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20an%20email%20from%20X%20on%20February%2020%20stating%20that%20%E2%80%98in%20the%20interest%20of%20transparency%2