ss-as-trump-rematch-looms%2Famp_articleshow%2F108295679.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbiden-to-give-high-stakes-address-as-trump-rematch-looms%2Famp_articleshow%2F108295679.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'What%20I%20Want%20Is%20Justice'%3A%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman's%20Speech%20That%20Changed%20History%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07140906%2F12109456696_e1f1a688fa_o.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Fifty-two%20years%20ago%2C%20on%20this%20day%2C%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Awami%20League%20in%20erstwhile%20East%20Pakistan%2C%20addressed%20a%20crowd%20of%20over%20two%20million%20people%20at%20Dhaka%E2%80%99s%20Ramna%20Race%20Course%20field%20in%20which%20he%20blew%20the%20bugle%20for%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20independence%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%207%2C%201971%2C%20Rahman%20told%20the%20people%20about%20West%20Pakistan%20barring%20his%20party%20from%20forming%20a%20government%20in%20spite%20of%20winning%20the%201970%20elections%20and%20launching%20atrocities%20on%20common%20citizens.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20struggle%20this%20time%20is%20for%20emancipation!%20The%20struggle%20this%20time%20is%20for%20independence!%E2%80%9D%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20ultimately%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20Bangladesh%20on%20March%2026%2C%201971%2C%20and%20Rahman%20became%20the%20father%20of%20the%20new%20nation%2C%20the%20Bangabandhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20full%20speech%20that%20changed%20the%20history%20of%20the%20sub-continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20dear%20brothers%20.%20.%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20come%20before%20you%20today%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20your%20know%20how%20hard%20we%20have%20tried.%20But%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20sadness%20that%20the%20streets%20of%20Dhaka%2C%20Chittagong%2C%20Khulna%2C%20Rangpur%20and%20Rajshahi%20are%20today%20being%20spattered%20with%20the%20blood%20of%20my%20brothers%2C%20and%20the%20cry%20we%20hear%20from%20the%20Bengali%20people%20is%20a%20cry%20for%20freedom%20a%20cry%20for%20survival%2C%20a%20cry%20for%20our%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20brought%20about%20an%20Awami%20League%20victory%20so%20you%20could%20see%20a%20constitutional%20government%20restored.%20The%20hope%20was%20that%20the%20elected%20representatives%20of%20the%20people%2C%20sitting%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly%2C%20would%20formulate%20a%20constitution%20that%20would%20assure%20that%20people%20of%20their%20economic%2C%20political%20and%20cultural%20emancipation.%20But%20now%2C%20with%20great%20sadness%20in%20my%20heart%2C%20I%20look%20back%20on%20the%20past%2023%20years%20of%20our%20history%20and%20see%20nothing%20but%20a%20history%20of%20the%20shedding%20of%20the%20blood%20of%20the%20Bengali%20people.%20Ours%20has%20been%20a%20history%20of%20continual%20lamentation%2C%20repeated%20bloodshed%20and%20innocent%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20gave%20blood%20in%201952%2C%20we%20won%20a%20mandate%20in%201954.%20But%20we%20were%20still%20not%20allowed%20to%20take%20up%20the%20reins%20of%20this%20country.%20In%201958%2C%20Ayub%20Khan%20clamped%20Martial%20Law%20on%20our%20people%20and%20enslaved%20us%20for%20the%20next%2010%20years.%20In%201966%2C%20during%20the%20Six-Point%20Movement%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20many%20were%20the%20young%20men%20and%20women%20whose%20lives%20were%20stilled%20by%20government%20bullets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20downfall%20of%20Ayub%2C%20Mr.%20Yahya%20Khan%20took%20over%20with%20the%20promise%20that%20he%20would%20restore%20constitutional%20rule%2C%20that%20he%20would%20restore%20democracy%20and%20return%20power%20to%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20agreed.%20But%20you%20all%20know%20of%20the%20events%20that%20took%20place%20after%20that%20I%20ask%20you%2C%20are%20we%20the%20ones%20to%20blame%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20know%2C%20I%20have%20been%20in%20contract%20with%20President%20Yahya%20Khan.%20As%20leader%20of%20the%20majority%20part%20in%20the%20national%20Assembly%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20to%20set%20February%2015%20as%20the%20day%20for%20its%20opening%20session.%20He%20did%20not%20accede%20to%20the%20request%20I%20made%20as%20leader%20of%20the%20majority%20party.%20Instead%2C%20he%20went%20along%20with%20the%20delay%20requested%20by%20the%20minority%20leader%20Mr.%20Bhutto%20and%20announced%20that%20the%20Assembly%20would%20be%20convened%20on%20the%203rd%20of%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20accepted%20that%2C%20agreed%20to%20join%20the%20deliberations.%20I%20even%20went%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20saying%20that%20we%2C%20despite%20our%20majority%2C%20would%20still%20listen%20to%20any%20sound%20ideas%20from%20the%20minority%2C%20even%20if%20it%20were%20a%20lone%20voice.%20I%20committed%20myself%20to%20the%20support%20of%20anything%20to%20bolster%20the%20restoration%20of%20a%20constitutional%20government.%20When%20Mr.%20Bhutto%20came%20to%20Dhaka%2C%20we%20met.%20We%20talked.%20He%20left%2C%20sing%20that%20the%20doors%20to%20negotiation%20were%20still%20open.%20Moulana%20Noorani%20and%20Moulana%20Mufti%20were%20among%20those%20West%20Pakistan%20parliamentarians%20who%20visited%20Dhaka%20and%20talked%20with%20me%20about%20an%20agreement%20on%20a%20constitutional%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20could%20not%20agree%20to%20any%20deviation%20from%20the%20Six%20Points.%20That%20right%20rested%20with%20the%20people.%20Come%2C%20I%20said%2C%20let%20us%20sit%20down%20and%20resolve%20matters.%20But%20Bhutto%E2%80%99s%20retort%20was%20that%20he%20would%20not%20allow%20himself%20to%20become%20hostage%20on%20two%20fronts.%20He%20predicted%20that%20if%20any%20West%20Pakistani%20members%20of%20Parliament%20were%20to%20come%20to%20Dhaka%2C%20the%20Assembly%20would%20be%20turned%20into%20a%20slaughterhouse.%20He%20added%20that%20if%20anyone%20were%20to%20participate%20in%20such%20a%20session%2C%20a%20countrywide%20agitation%20would%20be%20launched%20from%20Peshawar%20to%20Karachi%20and%20that%20ever%20business%20would%20be%20shut%20down%20in%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20assured%20him%20that%20the%20Assembly%20would%20be%20convened%20and%20despite%20the%20dire%20threats%2C%20West%20Pakistani%20leaders%20did%20come%20down%20to%20Dhaka.%20But%20suddenly%2C%20on%20March%20I%2C%20the%20session%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20an%20immediate%20outcry%20against%20this%20move%20by%20the%20people.%20I%20called%20for%20a%20hartal%20as%20a%20peaceful%20form%20of%20protest%20and%20the%20masses%20redial%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20response.%20And%20what%20did%20we%20get%20as%20a%20response%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20turned%20his%20guns%20on%20my%20helpless%20people%2C%20a%20people%20with%20no%20arms%20to%20defend%20themselves.%20These%20were%20the%20same%20arms%20that%20had%20been%20purchased%20with%20our%20own%20money%20to%20protect%20us%20from%20external%20enemies.%20But%20it%20is%20my%20own%20people%20who%20are%20being%20fired%20upon%20today.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20too%2C%20each%20time%20we%20the%20numerically%20larger%20segment%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20population-tried%20to%20assert%20our%20rights%20and%20control%20our%20destiny%2C%20the%20conspired%20against%20us%20and%20pounced%20upon%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20asked%20them%20this%20before%3A%20How%20can%20you%20make%20your%20own%20brothers%20the%20target%20of%20your%20bullets%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20Yahya%20Khan%20says%20that%20I%20had%20agreed%20to%20a%20Round%20Table%20Conference%20on%20the%2010th.%20Let%20me%20point%20out%20that%20is%20not%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20said%2C%20Mr.%20Yahya%20Khan%2C%20your%20are%20the%20President%20of%20this%20country.%20Come%20to%20Dhaka%2C%20come%20and%20see%20how%20our%20poor%20Bengali%20people%20have%20been%20mown%20down%20by%20your%20bullets%2C%20how%20the%20laps%20of%20our%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20have%20been%20robbed%20and%20left%20empty%20and%20bereft%2C%20how%20my%20helpless%20people%20have%20been%20slaughtered.%20Come%2C%20I%20said%2C%20come%20and%20see%20for%20yourself%20and%20then%20be%20the%20judge%20and%20decide.%20That%20is%20what%20I%20told%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20I%20had%20told%20him%20there%20would%20be%20no%20Round%20Table%20Conference.%20What%20Round%20Table%20Conference%2C%20whose%20Round%20Table%20Conference%3F%20You%20expect%20me%20to%20sit%20at%20a%20Round%20Table%20Conference%20with%20the%20very%20same%20people%20who%20have%20emptied%20the%20laps%20of%20my%20mothers%20and%20my%20sisters%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%203rd%2C%20at%20the%20Paltan%2C%20I%20called%20for%20a%20non-cooperation%20movement%20and%20the%20shutdown%20of%20offices%2C%20courts%20and%20revenue%20collection.%20You%20gave%20me%20full%20support.%20Then%20suddenly%2C%20without%20consulting%20me%20or%20even%20informing%20us%2C%20he%20met%20with%20one%20individual%20for%20five%20hours%20and%20then%20made%20a%20speech%20in%20which%20he%20trend%20all%20the%20blame%20on%20me%2C%20laid%20all%20the%20fault%20at%20the%20door%20of%20the%20Bengali%20people!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deadlock%20was%20created%20by%20Bhutto%2C%20yet%20the%20Bengalis%20are%20the%20ones%20facing%20the%20bullets!%20We%20face%20their%20guns%2C%20yet%20its%20our%20fault.%20We%20are%20the%20ones%20being%20bit%20by%20their%20bullets-%20and%20its%20still%20our%20fault!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20struggle%20this%20time%20is%20a%20struggle%20for%20emancipation%2C%20the%20struggle%20this%20time%20is%20a%20struggle%20for%20independence!%20Brothers%2C%20they%20have%20now%20called%20the%20Assembly%20to%20assassin%20on%20March%2025%2C%20with%20the%20streets%20not%20yet%20dry%20of%20the%20blood%20of%20my%20brothers.%20You%20have%20called%20the%20Assembly%2C%20but%20you%20must%20first%20agree%20to%20meet%20my%20demands.%20Martial%20Law%20must%20be%20withdrawn%3B%20the%20soldiers%20must%20return%20to%20their%20barracks%3B%20the%20murderers%20of%20my%20people%20must%20be%20redressed.%20And%20%E2%80%A6.%20Power%20must%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20elected%20representatives%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20then%20will%20we%20consider%20if%20we%20can%20take%20part%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly%20or%20not!%20Before%20these%20demands%20are%20met%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20question%20of%20our%20participating%20in%20this%20session%20of%20the%20Assembly.%20That%20is%20one%20right%20not%20give%20to%20me%20as%20part%20of%20my%20mandate%20from%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20told%20them%20earlier%2C%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20refuses%20to%20walk%20to%20the%20Assembly%20trading%20upon%20the%20fresh%20stains%20of%20his%20brothers%E2%80%99%20blood!%20Do%20you%2C%20my%20brothers%2C%20have%20complete%20faith%20in%20me%E2%80%A6.%3F%20%E2%80%A6.%20Let%20me%20the%20tell%20you%20that%20the%20Prime%20Ministership%20is%20not%20what%20I%20seek.%20What%20I%20want%20is%20justice%2C%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20land.%20They%20tempted%20me%20with%20the%20Prime%20Ministership%20but%20the%20failed%20to%20buy%20me%20over.%20Nor%20did%20the%20succeed%20in%20hanging%20me%20on%20the%20gallows%2C%20for%20your%20rescued%20me%20with%20your%20blood%20from%20the%20so-called%20conspiracy%20case.%20That%20day%2C%20right%20here%20at%20this%20racecourse%2C%20I%20had%20pledge%20to%20you%20that%20I%20would%20pay%20for%20this%20blood%20debt%20with%20my%20own%20blood.%20Do%20you%20remember%3F%20I%20am%20read%20today%20to%20fulfill%20that%20promise!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20now%20declare%20the%20closure%20of%20all%20the%20courts%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20educational%20institutions%20for%20an%20indefinite%20period%20of%20time.%20No%20one%20will%20report%20to%20their%20offices-%20that%20is%20my%20instruction%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20that%20the%20poor%20are%20not%20inconvenienced%2C%20rickshaws%2C%20trains%20and%20other%20transport%20will%20ply%20normally-except%20serving%20any%20needs%20of%20the%20armed%20forces.%20If%20the%20army%20does%20not%20respect%20this%2C%20I%20shall%20not%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Secretariat%2C%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20High%20Court%2C%20Judge%E2%80%99s%20Courts%2C%20and%20government%20and%20semi-government%20offices%20shall%20remain%20shut.%20Only%20banks%20ma%20open%20for%20two%20hours%20daily%20for%20business%20transactions.%20But%20no%20money%20shall%20be%20transmitted%20from%20East%20to%20West%20Pakistan.%20The%20Bengali%20people%20must%20stay%20calm%20during%20these%20times.%20Telegraph%20and%20telephone%20communications%20will%20be%20confined%20within%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20this%20land%20are%20facing%20elimination%2C%20so%20be%20on%20guard.%20If%20need%20be%2C%20we%20will%20bring%20everything%20to%20a%20total%20standstill%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6.%20Collect%20your%20salaries%20on%20time.%20If%20the%20salaries%20are%20held%20up%2C%20if%20a%20single%20bullet%20is%20fired%20upon%20us%20henceforth%2C%20if%20the%20murder%20of%20my%20people%20does%20not%20cease%2C%20I%20call%20upon%20you%20to%20turn%20ever%20home%20into%20a%20fortress%20against%20their%20onslaught.%20Use%20whatever%20you%20can%20put%20your%20hands%20on%20to%20confront%20this%20enemy.%20Ever%20last%20road%20must%20be%20blocked.%20We%20will%20deprive%20them%20of%20food%2C%20we%20will%20deprive%20them%20of%20water.%20Even%20if%20I%20am%20not%20around%20to%20give%20you%20the%20orders%2C%20and%20if%20my%20associates%20are%20also%20not%20to%20be%20found%2C%20I%20ask%20you%20to%20continue%20your%20movement%20unabated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20say%20to%20them%20again%2C%20you%20are%20my%20brothers%2C%20return%20now%20to%20the%20barracks%20where%20you%20belong%20and%20no%20one%20will%20bear%20any%20hostility%20toward%20you.%20Only%20do%20not%20attempt%20t