%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20her%20venture%20recycles%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339831%2Fjamshedpur-rajiv-sharma-alve-smart-air-fresheners-plastic-free-eco-friendly-temple-flower-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efloral%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20earns%20more%20than%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20The%20entrepreneur%2C%20now%2041%2C%20has%20also%20provided%20training%20to%20over%203%2C000%20women%20on%20making%20these%20products%20using%20floral%20waste%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20waste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20venture%20started%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam5-1709639330.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Poonam%20started%20recycling%20floral%20waste%20in%20June%202019%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam5-1709639330.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam5-1709639330-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam5-1709639330-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam5-1709639330-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam5-1709639330-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam5-1709639330-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343948%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPoonam%20started%20recycling%20floral%20waste%20in%20June%202019.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20harboured%20dreams%20of%20becoming%20a%20doctor%2C%20but%20life%20had%20other%20plans.%20Before%20she%20could%20complete%20her%20education%2C%20she%20was%20married.%20Soon%2C%20she%20had%20two%20children%20and%20life%20revolved%20around%20them.%20As%20the%20children%20started%20school%2C%20Poonam%20slowly%20restarted%20her%20education%20and%20pursued%20a%20BEd%20(Bachelor%20of%20Education)%20degree%20and%20entered%20a%20teacher%20training%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20pursue%20a%20career%20as%20a%20teacher.%20Busy%20with%20household%20chores%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20family%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20the%20time%20to%20socialise%20or%20build%20a%20strong%20friend%E2%80%99s%20circle.%20So%20when%20her%20children%20left%20for%20hostel%20in%202018%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20reclaim%20her%20life%20and%20build%20a%20better%20future%20for%20the%20coming%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20almost%20went%20through%20an%20existential%20crisis%2C%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20What%20was%20the%20purpose%20of%20my%20life%3F%20I%20was%20depressed%2C%20alone%2C%20without%20a%20clear%20trajectory%20of%20life.%20My%20mother%20asked%20me%20to%20visit%20a%20temple%20as%20she%20felt%20it%20would%20make%20me%20happy.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Pinky%2C%20too%2C%20was%20going%20through%20a%20tough%20time%20and%20asked%20me%20if%20we%20could%20do%20something%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Poonam%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20highlighted%20above%2C%20she%20found%20her%20answer%20at%20the%20temple%20that%20changed%20her%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20tonnes%20of%20flowers%20were%20being%20dumped%20into%20the%20river%20daily.%20I%20found%20a%20company%20that%20was%20recycling%20flowers%20and%20asked%20for%20their%20help.%20They%20asked%20for%2