20a%20way%20to%20become%20self-reliant%2C%20while%20helping%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20collects%20floral%20waste%20from%20over%2015%20temples%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20today%20and%20gets%20almost%20100%20kg%20of%20waste%20every%20three%20days.%20Besides%20dhoop%2C%20which%20is%20her%20bestseller%2C%20she%20makes%20idols%20and%20air%20fresheners.%20Her%20products%20range%20from%20Rs%2050-350%2C%20earning%20her%20a%20monthly%20income%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20Her%20dhoop%20stand%20and%20packaging%20too%2C%20is%20made%20from%20waste.%20She%20employs%205%20women%20at%20her%20unit%2C%20who%20she%20calls%20the%20%E2%80%98flower%20recyclers%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Poonam%2C%20this%20business%20helped%20her%20build%20her%20identity%20and%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20environment%20and%20lives%20of%20countless%20women.%20Her%20dream%20is%20to%20make%20India%20a%20country%20where%20not%20even%20one%20religious%20place%20throws%20flowers%20in%20the%20garbage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20all%20women%20like%20her%2C%20looking%20to%20fulfil%20their%20dream%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20get%20one%20opportunity%20in%20life%20to%20carve%20a%20path%20for%20ourselves.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20miss%20it.%20Live%20for%20yourself%20and%20do%20what%20makes%20you%20happy.%20The%20first%20step%20is%20always%20difficult%2C%20but%20once%20you%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20it%2C%20there%20is%20no%20looking%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAaruhi%20Enterprise%20products%20will%20soon%20be%20available%20on%20Amazon%20and%20Flipkart.%20You%20can%20also%20purchase%20them%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saveprithvi.com%2Fcategory%2Forganic-dhoop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Poonam%20Singh)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publishe