20worth%20after%20growing%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nidhi%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESure%20enough%2C%20just%20as%20the%20wise%20woman%20had%20predicted%2C%20Nidhi%20turned%20to%20her%20daadi%E2%80%99s%20recipe%20when%20she%20faced%20the%20massive%20challenge%20of%20hairfall.%20The%20duo%20made%20the%20oil%20together%2C%20which%20took%20an%20entire%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20tremendous%20hair%20fall.%20After%20using%20it%20for%20about%20two-three%20months%2C%20we%20found%20that%20our%20hairfall%20had%20greatly%20reduced%20and%20our%20hair%20was%20growing.%20I%20started%20making%20it%20for%20my%20daughter%20and%20our%20domestic%20help%2C%20who%20also%20found%20it%20greatly%20effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Tuteja-Dua%20family%20shifted%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Gurugram%2C%20into%20an%20apartment%20complex.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20Nidhi%20would%20find%20an%20opportunity%20to%20give%20shape%20to%20her%20desires.%20She%20found%20women%20here%20who%20were%20running%20small%20businesses%20from%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20mothers%2C%20Nidhi%2C%20too%2C%20had%20a%20burning%20desire%20to%20have%20a%20flourishing%20career.%20When%20she%20heard%20about%20these%20women%2C%20she%20found%20her%20window.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20join%20the%20office%20again.%20I%20missed%20my%20financial%20freedom%20and%20kept%20thinking%20of%20what%20I%20could%20do%20to%20reclaim%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajni%2C%20who%20had%20spent%20her%20life%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20children%2C%20followed%20by%20her%20grandchildren%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20harbour%20such%20aspirations%2C%20she%20shares.%20But%20when%20Nidhi%20asked%20for%20her%20help%2C%20the%20indulgent%20mother-in-law%2C%20went%20all%20in%20to%20support%20her%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20star