ny%20camera%20that%20came%20my%20way.%20My%20learning%20process%20involved%20making%20many%20mistakes%20and%20gaining%20a%20variety%20of%20insights%20from%20the%20people%20in%20my%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201170px)%20100vw%2C%201170px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pallas's%20Cat%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671.jpg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671-500x334.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671-768x513.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343886%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22781%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPallas%E2%80%99s%20cat%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECapturing%20these%20incredible%20images%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20the%20secret%20behind%20how%20he%20takes%20these%20photos%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20big%20secret.%20I%20just%20grab%20my%20camera%20and%20shoot%20whatever%20catches%20my%20eye.%20For%20wildlife%20shots%20more%20specifically%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20bit%20different.%20I%20head%20to%20places%20known%20for%20wildlife%2C%20wait%20for%20hours%20scanning%20the%20area%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20to%20show.%20Wildlife%20is%20unpredictable%2C%20you%20know%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20there%20are%20those%20times%20when%20a%20wild%20animal%20pops%20up%20out%20of%20nowhere%20and%20puts%20on%20a%20show.%20So%2C%20I%20try%20to%20always%20keep%20my%20eyes%20open%20ensuring%20that%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20miss%20an%20opportunity%20to%20capture%20something%20in%20the%20wild.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20opportunity%20arrived%20in%20the%20winter%20of%202020-2021%20when%20he%20captured%20a%20captivating%20photograph%20of%20a%20Himalayan%20Brown%20Bear%20surrounded%20by%20feral%20dogs.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20won%20the%20second%20runner-up%20prize%20(Conservation%20Issues)%20in%20the%20Nature%20inFocus%20Photography%20Contest%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201222px)%20100vw%2C%201222px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh--1709561747.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karamjeet's%20award-winning%20photo%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh--1709561747.jpeg%201222w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh--1709561747-300x191.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh--1709561747-500x319.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh--1709561747-768x490.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh--1709561747-150x96.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343887%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKaramjeet%E2%80%99s%20award-winning%20photo%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fww