20discuss%20the%20artwork%20sprawled%20out%20on%20it.%20The%20room%2C%20which%20was%20once%20only%20a%20place%20for%20assemblies%2C%20has%20now%20taken%20on%20a%20new%20avatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20the%20students%20appear%20to%20be%20marvelling%20at%20what%20they%20see.%20But%20a%20closer%20look%20will%20reveal%20they%20are%20blind.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337583%2Ftulsi-village-chhattisgarh-youtube-village-hummer-studios-being-chhattisgarhiya-alwa-jalwa-gold-cg04%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20front%20of%20them%20must%20thus%20assume%20a%20%E2%80%98tactile%E2%80%99%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20suffices%20to%20say%20that%20the%20art%20is%20novel%20in%20its%20creation.%20For%20one%2C%20it%20beckons%20the%20students%20to%20touch%20it%20to%20understand%20it%2C%20thus%20disrupting%20the%20traditional%20notion%20that%20art%20needs%20to%20be%20appreciated%20from%20a%20distance.%20For%20another%2C%20it%20acts%20as%20a%20medium%20for%20the%20children%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20culture%20of%20their%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBringing%20this%20to%20fruition%20is%20a%20project%20%E2%80%98Sparsh%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20initiative%20launched%20by%20Asian%20Paints%20and%20the%20St%2Bart%20India%20Foundation%20%E2%80%94%20a%20platform%20that%20contributes%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334508%2Finspiring-story-of-sex-worker-turned-artist-aravani-art-project-for-transgenders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20urban%20regeneration%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20community%20living%20through%20contemporary%20urban%20art%20projects.%20The%20project%20is%20rooted%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20art%20connects%20people%20through%20thoughts%20and%20feelings%20that%20cannot%20be%20expressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20siz